107
00:08:58,288 --> 00:09:00,499
Sergeant, save your breath.
中士，屏住呼吸。
zhōng   shì   píng   zhù   hū   xī

108
00:09:00,666 --> 00:09:02,084
See you.
再见。
zài   jiàn

109
00:09:08,090 --> 00:09:11,552
- Who are you looking for? - Does Francesco the printer live here?
- 您在寻找谁？ - 弗朗切斯科（Francesco）打印机是否住在这里？
nín   zài   xún   zhǎo   shuí   fú   lǎng   qiè   sī   kē   dǎ   yìn   jī   shì   fǒu   zhù   zài   zhè   lǐ

110
00:09:12,094 --> 00:09:14,429
- Yes, but he's out. - Know where he went?
- 是的，但是他不在。 - 知道他去了哪里？
shì   de   dàn   shì   tā   bù   zài   zhī   dào   tā   qù   le   nǎ   lǐ

111
00:09:14,596 --> 00:09:16,557
That's his business, not mine.
那是他的事，不是我的。
nà   shì   tā   de   shì   bù   shì   wǒ   de

112
00:09:17,057 --> 00:09:20,143
- Excuse me, but who are you? - What's it to you?
- 对不起，但是你是谁？ - 你是什么？
duì   bù   qǐ   dàn   shì   nǐ   shì   shuí   nǐ   shì   shén   me

113
00:09:20,310 --> 00:09:23,313
- You must be Pina. - How did you know?
- 您必须是Pina。 - 你怎么知道？
nín   bì   xū   shì   nǐ   zěn   me   zhī   dào

114
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:25,357
Francesco always talks about you.
弗朗切斯科总是谈论你。
fú   lǎng   qiè   sī   kē   zǒng   shì   tán   lùn   nǐ

115
00:09:25,524 --> 00:09:27,568
- So you're - - A friend.
- 所以你---朋友。
suǒ   yǐ   nǐ   péng   yǒu

116
00:09:27,734 --> 00:09:30,654
Stupid me! I thought you were police!
愚蠢的我！我以为你是警察！
yú   chǔn   de   wǒ   wǒ   yǐ   wèi   nǐ   shì   jǐng   chá

117
00:09:30,821 --> 00:09:33,365
What can I do for you? - I need to get in his apartment.
我能为你做什么？ - 我需要进入他的公寓。
wǒ   néng   wèi   nǐ   zuò   shén   me   wǒ   xū   yào   jìn   rù   tā   de   gōng   yù

118
00:09:33,574 --> 00:09:35,534
I'll get the key.
我会得到钥匙。
wǒ   huì   dé   dào   yào   shi

119
00:09:46,879 --> 00:09:49,214
Sorry. I couldn't find it.
对不起。我找不到。
duì   bù   qǐ   wǒ   zhǎo   bù   dào

120
00:09:49,381 --> 00:09:50,966
This way.
这边走。
zhè   biān   zǒu

121
00:09:56,346 --> 00:09:58,682
It's a mess, but -
这是一团糟，但是 -
zhè   shì   yī   tuán   zāo   dàn   shì

122
00:09:58,849 --> 00:10:00,267
It doesn't matter.
没关系。
méi   guān   xì

123
00:10:00,434 --> 00:10:04,021
Listen, do you know Don Pietro, the parish priest?
听着，你知道教区神父唐·彼得罗吗？
tīng   zhe   nǐ   zhī   dào   jiào   qū   shén   fù   táng   bǐ   dé   luó   ma

124
00:10:04,188 --> 00:10:05,439
I'd like to speak to him.
我想和他说话。
wǒ   xiǎng   hé   tā   shuō   huà

125
00:10:05,606 --> 00:10:08,066
- I'll go get him. - No, not you.
- 我去找他。 - 不，不是你。
wǒ   qù   zhǎo   tā   bù   bù   shì   nǐ

126
00:10:08,233 --> 00:10:10,110
- I'll send my boy. - Better.
- 我寄我的男孩。 - 更好的。
wǒ   jì   wǒ   de   nán   hái   gèng   hǎo   de

127
00:10:10,277 --> 00:10:12,279
Wait for me in there.
等我在那里。
děng   wǒ   zài   nà   lǐ

128
00:10:14,907 --> 00:10:17,117
Marcello!
马塞洛！
mǎ   sāi   luò

129
00:10:21,038 --> 00:10:21,997
What?
什么？
shén   me

130
00:10:22,164 --> 00:10:24,333
- Come down a minute. - I can't.
- 下来一分钟。 - 我不能。
xià   lái   yī   fēn   zhōng   wǒ   bù   néng

131
00:10:24,500 --> 00:10:27,920
- Go get Don Pietro, quick. - I'm busy!
- 快点去唐·彼得罗（Don Pietro）。 - 我很忙！
kuài   diǎn   qù   táng   bǐ   dé   luó   wǒ   hěn   máng

132
00:10:28,086 --> 00:10:29,796
I said come down here!
我说来这里！
wǒ   shuō   lái   zhè   lǐ

133
00:10:34,134 --> 00:10:36,887
I've told you not to go up to Romoletto's. It's dangerous.
我告诉过您不要去Romoletto的。这很危险。
wǒ   gào   sù   guò   nín   bù   yào   qù   de   zhè   hěn   wēi   xiǎn

134
00:10:37,054 --> 00:10:39,097
Go get Don Pietro. - What do I tell him?
去找唐·彼得罗。 - 我告诉他什么？
qù   zhǎo   táng   bǐ   dé   luó   wǒ   gào   sù   tā   shén   me

135
00:10:39,264 --> 00:10:41,975
To come here right away. Now move it.
马上来这里。现在移动它。
mǎ   shàng   lái   zhè   lǐ   xiàn   zài   yí   dòng   tā

136
00:10:42,476 --> 00:10:44,436
And don't fool around on the way.
而且不要在途中愚弄。
ér   qiě   bù   yào   zài   tú   zhōng   yú   nòng

137
00:10:49,483 --> 00:10:52,611
- Don Pietro will be here shortly. - Thanks.
- 唐·彼得罗（Don Pietro）很快就会在这里。 - 谢谢。
táng   bǐ   dé   luó   hěn   kuài   jiù   huì   zài   zhè   lǐ   xiè   xiè

138
00:10:54,363 --> 00:10:56,823
We stormed a bakery this morning.
今天早上我们冲了一家面包店。
jīn   tiān   zǎo   shàng   wǒ   men   chōng   le   yī   jiā   miàn   bāo   diàn

139
00:10:56,990 --> 00:10:58,742
Second one this week.
本周第二个。
běn   zhōu   dì   èr   gè

140
00:10:58,909 --> 00:11:00,911
How are the women?
女人怎么样？
nǚ   rén   zěn   me   yàng

141
00:11:01,245 --> 00:11:03,622
Some know why they're doing it,
有些人知道他们为什么这样做，
yǒu   xiē   rén   zhī   dào   tā   men   wèi   shén   me   zhè   yàng   zuò

142
00:11:03,789 --> 00:11:06,500
but most just grab all the bread they can.
但是大多数只是抓住他们可能的面包。
dàn   shì   dà   duō   shù   zhǐ   shì   zhuā   zhù   tā   men   kě   néng   de   miàn   bāo

143
00:11:07,209 --> 00:11:10,212
This morning someone filched some shoes and a scale.
今天早上，有人用鞋子和一块秤。
jīn   tiān   zǎo   shàng   yǒu   rén   yòng   xié   zi   hé   yī   kuài   chèng

144
00:11:10,379 --> 00:11:12,464
<i>I'd like to know who filched my stockings!</i>
<i>我想知道谁弄袜子了！</i>
wǒ   xiǎng   zhī   dào   shuí   nòng   wà   zi   le

145
00:11:13,298 --> 00:11:14,299
Excuse me.
打扰一下。
dǎ   rǎo   yī   xià

146
00:11:14,466 --> 00:11:16,844
I bet you did - Mr. Manfredi!
我敢打赌你做到了 - 曼弗雷迪先生！
wǒ   gǎn   dǎ   dǔ   nǐ   zuò   dào   le   màn   fú   léi   dí   xiān   shēng

147
00:11:17,010 --> 00:11:19,388
What are you doing here? Looking for me?
你在这里做什么？在找我吗？
nǐ   zài   zhè   lǐ   zuò   shén   me   zài   zhǎo   wǒ   ma

148
00:11:19,555 --> 00:11:20,639
That's right.
这是正确的。
zhè   shì   zhèng   què   de

149
00:11:20,806 --> 00:11:23,183
I met him on the stairs and let him in -
我在楼梯上遇到了他，让他进去 -
wǒ   zài   lóu   tī   shàng   yù   dào   le   tā   ràng   tā   jìn   qù

150
00:11:23,350 --> 00:11:25,310
You could have let me know!
你可以让我知道！
nǐ   kě   yǐ   ràng   wǒ   zhī   dào

151
00:11:25,477 --> 00:11:28,438
It doesn't matter. I just had a favor to ask.
没关系。我只是有一个忙。
méi   guān   xì   wǒ   zhǐ   shì   yǒu   yī   gè   máng

152
00:11:28,605 --> 00:11:30,816
You're fine just like that. Excuse us.
那样好。对不起。
nà   yàng   hǎo   duì   bù   qǐ

153
00:11:31,650 --> 00:11:34,653
You see Marina, right? - Yes, at the cabaret.
你看到码头，对吗？ - 是的，在歌舞表演。
nǐ   kàn   dào   mǎ   tóu   duì   ma   shì   de   zài   gē   wǔ   biǎo   yǎn

154
00:11:34,820 --> 00:11:37,364
Please tell her I can't see her for a few days.
请告诉她，几天我看不到她。
qǐng   gào   sù   tā   jǐ   tiān   wǒ   kàn   bù   dào   tā

155
00:11:37,531 --> 00:11:39,408
I'll phone if I can.
如果可以的话，我会打电话。
rú   guǒ   kě   yǐ   de   huà   wǒ   huì   dǎ   diàn   huà

156
00:11:39,575 --> 00:11:41,869
- Anything else? - No, nothing else.
- 还要别的吗？ - 不，别无其他。
hái   yào   bié   de   ma   bù   bié   wú   qí   tā

157
00:11:42,035 --> 00:11:44,329
Then good-bye now.
然后再见。
rán   hòu   zài   jiàn

158
00:11:45,289 --> 00:11:48,500
- Does she live with you? - She's my sister.
- 她和你住在一起吗？ - 她是我的妹妹。
tā   hé   nǐ   zhù   zài   yī   qǐ   ma   tā   shì   wǒ   de   mèi   mèi

159
00:11:48,709 --> 00:11:50,335
Surprised, huh?
惊讶，是吗？
jīng   yà   shì   ma

160
00:11:50,669 --> 00:11:55,007
I wonder what lies she's told you about where she lives.
我想知道她告诉你她住在哪里的谎言。
wǒ   xiǎng   zhī   dào   tā   gào   sù   nǐ   tā   zhù   zài   nǎ   lǐ   de   huǎng   yán

161
00:11:55,215 --> 00:11:59,219
She's ashamed of us "starving workers." Says she's an artist.
她为我们“挨饿的工人”感到羞耻。说她是一名艺术家。
tā   wèi   wǒ   men   āi   è   de   gōng   rén   gǎn   dào   xiū   chǐ   shuō   tā   shì   yī   míng   yì   shù   jiā

162
00:11:59,386 --> 00:12:01,471
But I wouldn't trade places with her.
但是我不会和她交易场所。
dàn   shì   wǒ   bù   huì   hé   tā   jiāo   yì   chǎng   suǒ

163
00:12:01,638 --> 00:12:04,725
Not because she's bad. She's just stupid.
不是因为她很糟糕。她只是愚蠢的。
bù   shì   yīn   wèi   tā   hěn   zāo   gāo   tā   zhǐ   shì   yú   chǔn   de

164
00:12:08,270 --> 00:12:11,231
But how do you know Laura?
但是你怎么知道劳拉？
dàn   shì   nǐ   zěn   me   zhī   dào   láo   lā

165
00:12:11,732 --> 00:12:14,276
Sorry. I'm being nosy.
对不起。我很喜欢。
duì   bù   qǐ   wǒ   hěn   xǐ   huān

166
00:12:14,443 --> 00:12:16,987
No, she's a good friend of a girl I know.
不，她是我认识的女孩的好朋友。
bù   tā   shì   wǒ   rèn   shí   de   nǚ   hái   de   hǎo   péng   yǒu

167
00:12:17,154 --> 00:12:18,822
- Marina? - You know her?
- 码头？ - 你知道她吗？
mǎ   tóu   nǐ   zhī   dào   tā   ma

168
00:12:19,406 --> 00:12:21,241
Since she was a baby!
因为她还是个孩子！
yīn   wèi   tā   hái   shì   gè   hái   zi

169
00:12:21,408 --> 00:12:25,537
Her mother was a concierge near my father's tinsmith shop.
她的母亲是我父亲的Tinsmith商店附近的礼宾服务。
tā   de   mǔ   qīn   shì   wǒ   fù   qīn   de   shāng   diàn   fù   jìn   de   lǐ   bīn   fú   wù

170
00:12:25,704 --> 00:12:28,332
She and Laura grew up together.
她和劳拉一起长大。
tā   hé   láo   lā   yī   qǐ   zhǎng   dà

171
00:12:28,999 --> 00:12:31,084
But please don't tell Marina
但请不要告诉码头
dàn   qǐng   bù   yào   gào   sù   mǎ   tóu

172
00:12:31,251 --> 00:12:33,587
what I said.
我说的。
wǒ   shuō   de

173
00:12:33,754 --> 00:12:35,923
Don't worry. I won't be seeing her again.
不用担心。我不会再见到她。
bù   yòng   dān   xīn   wǒ   bù   huì   zài   jiàn   dào   tā

174
00:12:36,089 --> 00:12:37,090
Why?
为什么？
wèi   shén   me

175
00:12:37,257 --> 00:12:41,428
I just feel it's time to end it. It's gone on too long anyway.
我只是觉得是时候结束它了。无论如何，它已经走了太久了。
wǒ   zhǐ   shì   jué   dé   shì   shí   hòu   jié   shù   tā   le   wú   lùn   rú   hé   tā   yǐ   jīng   zǒu   le   tài   jiǔ   le

176
00:12:42,095 --> 00:12:44,932
- Have you known her long? - Four months.
- 你认识她很久了吗？ - 四个月。
nǐ   rèn   shí   tā   hěn   jiǔ   le   ma   sì   gè   yuè

177
00:12:45,098 --> 00:12:49,561
I'd just arrived in Rome. She used to eat in a certain restaurant.
我刚到罗马。她曾经在一家餐厅吃饭。
wǒ   gāng   dào   luó   mǎ   tā   céng   jīng   zài   yī   jiā   cān   tīng   chī   fàn

178
00:12:49,728 --> 00:12:52,231
One day the air-raid alarm went off, and everyone ran.
有一天，空袭警报响了，每个人都跑了。
yǒu   yī   tiān   kōng   xí   jǐng   bào   xiǎng   le   měi   gè   rén   dōu   pǎo   le

179
00:12:52,397 --> 00:12:54,399
Just she and I were left.
只是她和我离开了。
zhǐ   shì   tā   hé   wǒ   lí   kāi   le

180
00:12:54,566 --> 00:12:56,777
She just laughed. Wasn't scared at all.
她只是笑了。一点都不害怕。
tā   zhǐ   shì   xiào   le   yī   diǎn   dōu   bù   hài   pà

181
00:12:56,944 --> 00:12:59,863
- And you fell in love. - It happens.
- 你坠入爱河。 - 发生。
nǐ   zhuì   rù   ài   hé   fā   shēng

182
00:13:00,280 --> 00:13:02,157
Yes, it does.
是的，确实如此。
shì   de   què   shí   rú   cǐ

183
00:13:03,116 --> 00:13:05,327
But she's not the woman for me.
但是她不是我的女人。
dàn   shì   tā   bù   shì   wǒ   de   nǚ   rén

184
00:13:05,494 --> 00:13:09,081
Perhaps if I'd met her when she was younger.
也许如果我小时候我会见她。
yě   xǔ   rú   guǒ   wǒ   xiǎo   shí   hòu   wǒ   huì   jiàn   tā

185
00:13:09,248 --> 00:13:12,835
A woman can change, especially when she's in love.
女人可以改变，尤其是当她恋爱时。
nǚ   rén   kě   yǐ   gǎi   biàn   yóu   qí   shì   dāng   tā   liàn   ài   shí

186
00:13:13,001 --> 00:13:15,003
Who told you she's in love?
谁告诉你她恋爱了？
shuí   gào   sù   nǐ   tā   liàn   ài   le

187
00:13:15,170 --> 00:13:17,256
Why shouldn't she be?
她为什么不这样？
tā   wèi   shén   me   bù   zhè   yàng

188
00:13:17,464 --> 00:13:20,634
Heavens, I didn't even offer you coffee.
天堂，我什至没有给你咖啡。
tiān   táng   wǒ   shén   zhì   méi   yǒu   gěi   nǐ   kā   fēi

189
00:13:20,801 --> 00:13:23,136
It's no bother. It'll only take a moment.
没什么打扰。只需要一点时间。
méi   shén   me   dǎ   rǎo   zhǐ   xū   yào   yī   diǎn   shí   jiān

190
00:13:23,303 --> 00:13:25,138
Mind you, "coffee" in name only.
请注意，只有名字的“咖啡”。
qǐng   zhù   yì   zhǐ   yǒu   míng   zì   de   kā   fēi

191
00:13:46,994 --> 00:13:49,663
Stop all this ruckus!
停止所有这些骚动！
tíng   zhǐ   suǒ   yǒu   zhè   xiē   sāo   dòng

192
00:14:00,632 --> 00:14:02,676
I told you before: No rough stuff.
我以前告诉过你：没有粗糙的东西。
wǒ   yǐ   qián   gào   sù   guò   nǐ   méi   yǒu   cū   cāo   de   dōng   xī

193
00:14:02,843 --> 00:14:04,636
Watch out, Don Pietro!
当心，唐·彼得罗（Don Pietro）！
dāng   xīn   táng   bǐ   dé   luó

194
00:14:09,850 --> 00:14:12,644
Well, well. It's a miracle to see you here.
好吧，好吧。在这里见到你是一个奇迹。
hǎo   ba   hǎo   ba   zài   zhè   lǐ   jiàn   dào   nǐ   shì   yī   gè   qí   jì

195
00:14:12,811 --> 00:14:17,107
- My mother sent me. - She's smart. It'll do you good.
- 我妈妈寄给我。 - 她很聪明。它会很好。
wǒ   mā   mā   jì   gěi   wǒ   tā   hěn   cōng   míng   tā   huì   hěn   hǎo

196
00:14:17,274 --> 00:14:19,026
Don Pietro, let me finish.
唐·皮特罗（Don Pietro），让我结束。
táng   pí   tè   luó   ràng   wǒ   jié   shù

197
00:14:19,193 --> 00:14:22,362
She says to come quickly. It's important.
她说要快。这很重要。
tā   shuō   yào   kuài   zhè   hěn   zhòng   yào

198
00:14:22,529 --> 00:14:25,407
- What? - I don't know. She acted mysterious.
- 什么？ - 我不知道。她举止神秘。
shén   me   wǒ   bù   zhī   dào   tā   jǔ   zhǐ   shén   mì

199
00:14:25,574 --> 00:14:28,368
But I think someone's in Francesco's apartment.
但是我认为有人在弗朗切斯科的公寓里。
dàn   shì   wǒ   rèn   wèi   yǒu   rén   zài   fú   lǎng   qiè   sī   kē   de   gōng   yù   lǐ

200
00:14:28,911 --> 00:14:31,121
Very well. Let's go.
很好。我们走吧。
hěn   hǎo   wǒ   men   zǒu   ba

201
00:14:33,207 --> 00:14:34,583
Gilberto.
吉尔伯托。
jí   ěr   bó   tuō

202
00:14:35,542 --> 00:14:38,045
You, out of the way.
你，避开了。
nǐ   bì   kāi   le

203
00:14:38,670 --> 00:14:41,465
Agostino will be here soon. You referee.
Agostino很快就会在这里。你裁判。
hěn   kuài   jiù   huì   zài   zhè   lǐ   nǐ   cái   pàn

204
00:14:41,632 --> 00:14:43,550
And behave yourselves.
并表现自己。
bìng   biǎo   xiàn   zì   jǐ

205
00:14:44,009 --> 00:14:44,968
Here!
这里！
zhè   lǐ

206
00:14:45,135 --> 00:14:48,096
Come here. Why are you always running off?
来这里。你为什么总是逃跑？
lái   zhè   lǐ   nǐ   wèi   shén   me   zǒng   shì   táo   pǎo

207
00:15:23,340 --> 00:15:25,300
Why don't you come around anymore?
你为什么不走了？
nǐ   wèi   shén   me   bù   zǒu   le

208
00:15:25,467 --> 00:15:29,263
- This is no time for catechism. - What are you saying?
- 这不是教理主义的时间。 - 你在说什么？
zhè   bù   shì   jiào   lǐ   zhǔ   yì   de   shí   jiān   nǐ   zài   shuō   shén   me

209
00:15:29,429 --> 00:15:31,014
You priests can't understand,
你的牧师听不懂，
nǐ   de   mù   shī   tīng   bù   dǒng

210
00:15:31,181 --> 00:15:34,518
but we have to close ranks against the common enemy.
但是我们必须对共同敌人进行关闭。
dàn   shì   wǒ   men   bì   xū   duì   gòng   tóng   dí   rén   jìn   xíng   guān   bì

211
00:15:34,685 --> 00:15:36,562
Who tells you these things?
谁告诉你这些事情？
shuí   gào   sù   nǐ   zhè   xiē   shì   qíng

212
00:15:36,728 --> 00:15:38,063
Romoletto.
Romoletto。

213
00:15:38,230 --> 00:15:39,731
Romoletto?
romoletto？

214
00:15:39,898 --> 00:15:42,192
Don Pietro, please don't tell anyone.
唐·皮特罗（Don Pietro），请不要告诉任何人。
táng   pí   tè   luó   qǐng   bù   yào   gào   sù   rèn   hé   rén

215
00:15:44,278 --> 00:15:46,363
Here comes Purgatory.
炼狱来了。
liàn   yù   lái   le

216
00:15:48,740 --> 00:15:50,075
Don Pietro.
唐·皮特罗（Don Pietro）。
táng   pí   tè   luó

217
00:15:50,242 --> 00:15:52,661
- What have you got there? - I've been shopping.
- 你到达了什么？ - 我一直在购物。
nǐ   dào   dá   le   shén   me   wǒ   yī   zhí   zài   gòu   wù

218
00:15:52,828 --> 00:15:55,372
What a load of bread! Was that your whole ration book?
多么的面包！那是您的整本评估书吗？
duō   me   de   miàn   bāo   nà   shì   nín   de   zhěng   běn   píng   gū   shū   ma

219
00:15:55,539 --> 00:15:57,040
Not even one coupon.
甚至没有一张优惠券。
shèn   zhì   méi   yǒu   yī   zhāng   yōu   huì   quàn

220
00:15:57,207 --> 00:15:58,458
Why all this bread?
为什么所有这些面包？
wèi   shén   me   suǒ   yǒu   zhè   xiē   miàn   bāo

221
00:15:58,625 --> 00:16:01,253
- They were celebrating this morning. - What?
- 他们今天早上庆祝。 - 什么？
tā   men   jīn   tiān   zǎo   shàng   qìng   zhù   shén   me

222
00:16:01,420 --> 00:16:04,840
I don't know what holiday. Even the baker didn't know.
我不知道什么假期。甚至面包师都不知道。
wǒ   bù   zhī   dào   shén   me   jiǎ   qī   shèn   zhì   miàn   bāo   shī   dōu   bù   zhī   dào

223
00:16:05,007 --> 00:16:07,301
Excuse me. I have to go.
打扰一下。我得走了。
dǎ   rǎo   yī   xià   wǒ   dé   zǒu   le

224
00:16:07,467 --> 00:16:10,387
- What holiday could it be? - I don't understand.
- 可以是什么假期？ - 我不明白。
kě   yǐ   shì   shén   me   jiǎ   qī   wǒ   bù   míng   bái

225
00:16:10,554 --> 00:16:12,431
I hope my mother knew about it.
我希望我妈妈知道这一点。
wǒ   xī   wàng   wǒ   mā   mā   zhī   dào   zhè   yī   diǎn

226
00:16:14,349 --> 00:16:15,851
Here you go.
干得好。
gàn   dé   hǎo

227
00:16:16,226 --> 00:16:19,771
It's not very good, but at least it's hot. Drink up.
这不是很好，但至少很热。喝酒。
zhè   bù   shì   hěn   hǎo   dàn   zhì   shǎo   hěn   rè   hē   jiǔ

228
00:16:19,938 --> 00:16:22,816
Thanks. Francesco says you two are getting married.
谢谢。弗朗切斯科说，你们两个要结婚。
xiè   xiè   fú   lǎng   qiè   sī   kē   shuō   nǐ   men   liǎng   gè   yào   jié   hūn

229
00:16:22,983 --> 00:16:26,945
The wedding's a little late... in my condition.
婚礼有点晚...在我的情况下。
hūn   lǐ   yǒu   diǎn   wǎn   zài   wǒ   de   qíng   kuàng   xià

230
00:16:27,112 --> 00:16:32,576
But we set a date a long time ago and had to keep postponing it.
但是我们很久以前就设定了约会，不得不继续推迟它。
dàn   shì   wǒ   men   hěn   jiǔ   yǐ   qián   jiù   shè   dìng   le   yuē   huì   bù   dé   bù   jì   xù   tuī   chí   tā

231
00:16:32,743 --> 00:16:34,786
- When is it? - Tomorrow.
- 什么时候？ - 明天。
shén   me   shí   hòu   míng   tiān

232
00:16:34,953 --> 00:16:37,623
- I'll need to get you a present. - Heavens no!
- 我需要给你礼物。 - 天堂不！
wǒ   xū   yào   gěi   nǐ   lǐ   wù   tiān   táng   bù

233
00:16:37,789 --> 00:16:41,585
It's just a wartime wedding. Don Pietro says a few words and it's over.
这只是一场战时婚礼。唐·彼得罗（Don Pietro）说了几句话，而且结束了。
zhè   zhǐ   shì   yī   chǎng   zhàn   shí   hūn   lǐ   táng   bǐ   dé   luó   shuō   le   jǐ   jù   huà   ér   qiě   jié   shù   le

234
00:16:41,752 --> 00:16:43,962
- You're marrying in the church? - Yes.
- 您在教堂结婚吗？ - 是的。
nín   zài   jiào   táng   jié   hūn   ma   shì   de

235
00:16:44,129 --> 00:16:46,840
Francesco didn't want to, but I told him
弗朗切斯科不想，但我告诉他
fú   lǎng   qiè   sī   kē   bù   xiǎng   dàn   wǒ   gào   sù   tā

236
00:16:47,007 --> 00:16:49,551
better Don Pietro, who's at least one of our own,
最好的唐·彼得罗（Don Pietro），至少是我们自己的人，
zuì   hǎo   de   táng   bǐ   dé   luó   zhì   shǎo   shì   wǒ   men   zì   jǐ   de   rén

237
00:16:49,718 --> 00:16:52,721
then some Fascist at city hall, don't you think?
然后在市政厅一些法西斯主义者，你不觉得吗？
rán   hòu   zài   shì   zhèng   tīng   yī   xiē   fǎ   xī   sī   zhǔ   yì   zhě   nǐ   bù   jué   dé   ma

238
00:16:53,263 --> 00:16:55,182
In a way you're right.
从某种意义上说，你是对的。
cóng   mǒu   zhǒng   yì   yì   shàng   shuō   nǐ   shì   duì   de

239
00:16:55,349 --> 00:16:58,977
The truth is, I believe in God.
事实是，我相信上帝。
shì   shí   shì   wǒ   xiāng   xìn   shàng   dì

240
00:16:59,811 --> 00:17:01,647
Do you work?
你工作了吗？
nǐ   gōng   zuò   le   ma

241
00:17:01,813 --> 00:17:04,191
I used to. In a fuse factory.
我曾经。在保险丝工厂。
wǒ   céng   jīng   zài   bǎo   xiǎn   sī   gōng   chǎng

242
00:17:04,358 --> 00:17:08,612
But they threw us out. The Germans are taking everything.
但是他们把我们赶了出去。德国人正在夺走一切。
dàn   shì   tā   men   bǎ   wǒ   men   gǎn   le   chū   qù   dé   guó   rén   zhèng   zài   duó   zǒu   yī   qiè

243
00:17:11,031 --> 00:17:12,658
It must be Don Pietro.
它一定是唐·皮特罗（Don Pietro）。
tā   yī   dìng   shì   táng   pí   tè   luó

244
00:17:19,206 --> 00:17:21,083
Hello, Don Pietro.
你好，唐·彼得罗。
nǐ   hǎo   táng   bǐ   dé   luó

245
00:17:21,500 --> 00:17:24,336
Excuse me. I'll be across the hall.
打扰一下。我会在大厅对面。
dǎ   rǎo   yī   xià   wǒ   huì   zài   dà   tīng   duì   miàn

246
00:17:24,503 --> 00:17:27,005
- Thanks for coming. - Don't mention it.
- 感谢您的到来。 - 不要提及。
gǎn   xiè   nín   de   dào   lái   bù   yào   tí   jí

247
00:17:28,632 --> 00:17:30,843
- What's this? - Who's in there?
- 这是什么？ - 谁在那里？
zhè   shì   shén   me   shuí   zài   nà   lǐ

248
00:17:31,009 --> 00:17:34,596
None of your business. Go get some water. Hurry up.
关你屁事。去获取水。赶快。
guān   nǐ   pì   shì   qù   huò   qǔ   shuǐ   gǎn   kuài

249
00:17:47,818 --> 00:17:49,987
- I have to talk to you. - Come on.
- 我必须和你说话。 - 快点。
wǒ   bì   xū   hé   nǐ   shuō   huà   kuài   diǎn

250
00:17:50,153 --> 00:17:52,531
There are 500 men in the hills above Tagliacozzo.
塔格利亚科佐上方的山丘上有500人。
tǎ   gé   lì   yà   kē   zuǒ   shàng   fāng   de   shān   qiū   shàng   yǒu   rén

251
00:17:52,698 --> 00:17:55,075
They're good men. We can't abandon them.
他们是好人。我们不能放弃他们。
tā   men   shì   hǎo   rén   wǒ   men   bù   néng   fàng   qì   tā   men

252
00:17:55,242 --> 00:17:59,204
One of them will be waiting at 6:00 on the Tiburtine bridge.
其中一个将在Tiburtine桥上6:00等待。
qí   zhōng   yī   gè   jiāng   zài   qiáo   shàng   děng   dài

253
00:17:59,371 --> 00:18:03,250
I'd better not go, because I've been denounced.
我最好不要去，因为我被谴责。
wǒ   zuì   hǎo   bù   yào   qù   yīn   wèi   wǒ   bèi   qiǎn   zé

254
00:18:03,417 --> 00:18:06,128
Besides, the curfew's at 5:00 now.
此外，宵禁现在为5:00。
cǐ   wài   xiāo   jìn   xiàn   zài   wèi

255
00:18:06,295 --> 00:18:07,671
I see.
我懂了。
wǒ   dǒng   le

256
00:18:09,006 --> 00:18:11,508
I'll go. - I knew you would.
我去。 - 我知道你会的。
wǒ   qù   wǒ   zhī   dào   nǐ   huì   de

257
00:18:11,800 --> 00:18:13,760
- What's the message? - No message.
- 消息是什么？ - 没有消息。
xiāo   xī   shì   shén   me   méi   yǒu   xiāo   xī

258
00:18:13,927 --> 00:18:16,513
It's money from the military committee.
这是军事委员会的钱。
zhè   shì   jūn   shì   wěi   yuán   huì   de   qián

259
00:18:17,431 --> 00:18:19,141
Is it too much to ask?
要问太多了吗？
yào   wèn   tài   duō   le   ma

260
00:18:19,308 --> 00:18:22,561
No, too little, even, for those sacrificing their lives.
不，对于那些牺牲生命的人来说太少了。
bù   duì   yú   nà   xiē   xī   shēng   shēng   mìng   de   rén   lái   shuō   tài   shǎo   le

261
00:18:22,728 --> 00:18:24,521
How will I recognize him?
我将如何认出他？
wǒ   jiāng   rú   hé   rèn   chū   tā

262
00:18:24,688 --> 00:18:27,733
He'll whistle that song "Morning in Florence."
他会吹口哨那首歌“佛罗伦萨的早晨”。
tā   huì   chuī   kǒu   shào   nà   shǒu   gē   fú   luó   lún   sà   de   zǎo   chén

263
00:18:27,941 --> 00:18:30,777
But of course you wouldn't know it. - How's it go?
但是，您当然不会知道。 - 怎么样？
dàn   shì   nín   dāng   rán   bù   huì   zhī   dào   zěn   me   yàng

264
00:18:30,944 --> 00:18:32,446
Like this.
像这样。
xiàng   zhè   yàng

265
00:18:38,160 --> 00:18:39,953
Everyone's singing it.
每个人都在唱歌。
měi   gè   rén   dōu   zài   chàng   gē

266
00:19:00,807 --> 00:19:02,643
Hello, Father.
你好，父亲。
nǐ   hǎo   fù   qīn

267
00:19:02,976 --> 00:19:04,770
How can I help you?
我怎么帮你？
wǒ   zěn   me   bāng   nǐ

268
00:19:05,354 --> 00:19:07,856
Would you have a statue of St. Anthony the Abbot?
你会有一个方丈圣安东尼雕像吗？
nǐ   huì   yǒu   yī   gè   fāng   zhàng   shèng   ān   dōng   ní   diāo   xiàng   ma

269
00:19:08,023 --> 00:19:11,360
Sorry, but there's not much demand for those now.
抱歉，但现在对这些需求不多。
bào   qiàn   dàn   xiàn   zài   duì   zhè   xiē   xū   qiú   bù   duō

270
00:19:11,527 --> 00:19:13,612
But I have a St. Roch.
但是我有一个圣罗克。
dàn   shì   wǒ   yǒu   yī   gè   shèng   luó   kè

271
00:19:14,154 --> 00:19:16,156
Thanks, but I'm not interested.
谢谢，但我不感兴趣。
xiè   xiè   dàn   wǒ   bù   gǎn   xīng   qù

272
00:19:16,323 --> 00:19:19,576
Not interested in a saint like St. Roch?
对像圣罗奇这样的圣人不感兴趣吗？
duì   xiàng   shèng   luó   qí   zhè   yàng   de   shèng   rén   bù   gǎn   xīng   qù   ma

273
00:19:19,952 --> 00:19:20,911
Step inside.
走进来。
zǒu   jìn   lái

274
00:19:21,078 --> 00:19:22,746
Come and see.
来看看。
lái   kàn   kàn

275
00:19:25,541 --> 00:19:28,627
It's a beauty too. - Let's have a look.
这也是美女。 - 让我们看看。
zhè   yě   shì   měi   nǚ   ràng   wǒ   men   kàn   kàn

276
00:19:29,002 --> 00:19:30,504
I'll be going.
我要去的。
wǒ   yào   qù   de

277
00:19:30,671 --> 00:19:32,756
Remember to stop by Chiurazzi's.
记住要停下来chiurazzi的。
jì   zhù   yào   tíng   xià   lái   de

278
00:19:32,923 --> 00:19:34,675
I'll give you a good price.
我给你一个好的价格。
wǒ   gěi   nǐ   yī   gè   hǎo   de   jià   gé

279
00:19:34,842 --> 00:19:37,511
I need to speak to Francesco.
我需要与弗朗切斯科说话。
wǒ   xū   yào   yǔ   fú   lǎng   qiè   sī   kē   shuō   huà

280
00:19:37,678 --> 00:19:40,305
The man with the tight shoes sent me.
那个穿紧鞋的男人送我了。
nà   gè   chuān   jǐn   xié   de   nán   rén   sòng   wǒ   le

281
00:19:41,348 --> 00:19:42,975
Wait a moment.
稍等。
shāo   děng

282
00:20:00,534 --> 00:20:03,036
Come in, Father. They're waiting for you.
进来，父亲。他们在等你。
jìn   lái   fù   qīn   tā   men   zài   děng   nǐ

283
00:20:15,174 --> 00:20:16,800
Down these stairs.
下楼梯。
xià   lóu   tī

284
00:20:23,056 --> 00:20:25,726
Don Pietro, what's happened?
唐·彼得罗（Don Pietro），发生了什么事？
táng   bǐ   dé   luó   fā   shēng   le   shén   me   shì

285
00:20:25,893 --> 00:20:28,979
Nothing serious, thank heavens, but it might have been.
没什么严重的，感谢天堂，但可能已经如此。
méi   shén   me   yán   zhòng   de   gǎn   xiè   tiān   táng   dàn   kě   néng   yǐ   jīng   rú   cǐ

286
00:20:29,146 --> 00:20:32,941
The SS were at Manfredi's last night. - We know. Where is he now?
党卫军昨晚在曼弗雷迪（Manfredi）的。 - 我们知道。他现在在哪里？
dǎng   wèi   jūn   zuó   wǎn   zài   màn   fú   léi   dí   de   wǒ   men   zhī   dào   tā   xiàn   zài   zài   nǎ   lǐ

287
00:20:33,108 --> 00:20:34,776
At your place.
在你家。
zài   nǐ   jiā

288
00:20:34,943 --> 00:20:37,738
Pina let him in. He'll be staying a few days.
皮娜让他进去。他将待几天。
pí   nà   ràng   tā   jìn   qù   tā   jiāng   dài   jǐ   tiān

289
00:20:39,781 --> 00:20:41,700
He gave me this note.
他给了我这个笔记。
tā   gěi   le   wǒ   zhè   gè   bǐ   jì

290
00:20:41,867 --> 00:20:46,246
I wanted to send him to the Passionist monks. He'd be safer there.
我想把他送到热情的僧侣。他会在那里更安全。
wǒ   xiǎng   bǎ   tā   sòng   dào   rè   qíng   de   sēng   lǚ   tā   huì   zài   nà   lǐ   gèng   ān   quán

291
00:20:46,413 --> 00:20:49,333
But he said he'd be too isolated.
但是他说他太孤立了。
dàn   shì   tā   shuō   tā   tài   gū   lì   le

292
00:20:49,500 --> 00:20:50,667
It's true.
是的。
shì   de

293
00:20:50,834 --> 00:20:54,087
But he's in greater danger now that he's been denounced.
但是，由于被谴责，他正处于更大的危险之中。
dàn   shì   yóu   yú   bèi   qiǎn   zé   tā   zhèng   chù   yú   gèng   dà   de   wēi   xiǎn   zhī   zhōng

294
00:20:54,296 --> 00:20:57,799
Yes, Father, but if our few men all hid in monasteries -
是的，父亲，但是如果我们的几个男人都藏在修道院里 -
shì   de   fù   qīn   dàn   shì   rú   guǒ   wǒ   men   de   jǐ   gè   nán   rén   dōu   cáng   zài   xiū   dào   yuàn   lǐ

295
00:20:57,966 --> 00:21:00,969
- I understand. - Allow me. This is our editor.
- 我明白。 - 请允许我。这是我们的编辑。
wǒ   míng   bái   qǐng   yǔn   xǔ   wǒ   zhè   shì   wǒ   men   de   biān   jí

296
00:21:01,136 --> 00:21:02,679
Pleased to meet you.
很高兴认识你。
hěn   gāo   xīng   rèn   shí   nǐ

297
00:21:02,846 --> 00:21:04,973
Same here. I've heard a lot about you.
同样在这里。我听说了很多你。
tóng   yàng   zài   zhè   lǐ   wǒ   tīng   shuō   le   hěn   duō   nǐ

298
00:21:05,140 --> 00:21:07,434
That's not good for my modesty
那对我的谦虚不利
nà   duì   wǒ   de   qiān   xū   bù   lì

299
00:21:07,601 --> 00:21:09,686
or my health.
或我的健康。
huò   wǒ   de   jiàn   kāng

300
00:21:09,853 --> 00:21:12,814
We appreciate all you've done for us.
感谢您为我们所做的一切。
gǎn   xiè   nín   wèi   wǒ   men   suǒ   zuò   de   yī   qiè

301
00:21:12,981 --> 00:21:16,318
It's my duty to help those in need.
帮助有需要的人是我的责任。
bāng   zhù   yǒu   xū   yào   de   rén   shì   wǒ   de   zé   rèn

302
00:21:16,485 --> 00:21:18,153
Step into my office?
走进我的办公室？
zǒu   jìn   wǒ   de   bàn   gōng   shì

303
00:21:36,839 --> 00:21:38,298
Here you are, Father.
父亲，你在这里。
fù   qīn   nǐ   zài   zhè   lǐ

304
00:21:38,465 --> 00:21:41,760
Manfredi said it would be money.
曼弗雷迪说这是金钱。
màn   fú   léi   dí   shuō   zhè   shì   jīn   qián

305
00:21:42,094 --> 00:21:44,680
There's not much to read in those books.
这些书中没有什么可阅读的。
zhè   xiē   shū   zhōng   méi   yǒu   shén   me   kě   yuè   dú   de

306
00:21:45,639 --> 00:21:47,516
What do you mean?
你是什​​么意思？
nǐ   shì   shén   me   yì   sī

307
00:21:55,691 --> 00:21:58,569
Is it all like that? - A thousand pages.
都是这样吗？ - 一千页。
dōu   shì   zhè   yàng   ma   yī   qiān   yè

308
00:22:00,028 --> 00:22:02,322
- One million lire. - Precisely.
- 一百万个lire。 - 正是。
yī   bǎi   wàn   gè   zhèng   shì

309
00:23:01,256 --> 00:23:02,466
Who is it?
是谁？
shì   shuí

310
00:23:02,633 --> 00:23:04,760
<i>It's me. Open up.</i>
<i>是我。打开。</i>
shì   wǒ   dǎ   kāi

311
00:23:16,271 --> 00:23:19,233
- Guess who I saw this morning. - I don't care.
- 猜猜我今天早上见到谁。 - 我不在乎。
cāi   cāi   wǒ   jīn   tiān   zǎo   shàng   jiàn   dào   shuí   wǒ   bù   zài   hū

312
00:23:19,441 --> 00:23:22,277
- Manfredi. He came to see me. - You? Where?
- 曼弗雷迪。他来见我。 - 你？在哪里？
màn   fú   léi   dí   tā   lái   jiàn   wǒ   nǐ   zài   nǎ   lǐ

313
00:23:22,444 --> 00:23:23,946
At my place.
在我的位置。
zài   wǒ   de   wèi   zhì

314
00:23:24,279 --> 00:23:26,031
What did he want?
他想要什么？
tā   xiǎng   yào   shén   me

315
00:23:26,198 --> 00:23:29,368
He said he can't see you for a few days
他说他几天看不到你
tā   shuō   tā   jǐ   tiān   kàn   bù   dào   nǐ

316
00:23:29,535 --> 00:23:31,495
and that he'll call if necessary.
并且他会在必要时打电话。
bìng   qiě   tā   huì   zài   bì   yào   shí   dǎ   diàn   huà

317
00:23:31,662 --> 00:23:33,455
Nothing else?
别无其他吗？
bié   wú   qí   tā   ma

318
00:23:33,747 --> 00:23:35,749
He didn't explain?
他没有解释？
tā   méi   yǒu   jiě   shì

319
00:23:35,916 --> 00:23:38,043
No, and I didn't ask.
不，我没有问。
bù   wǒ   méi   yǒu   wèn

320
00:23:38,252 --> 00:23:41,171
I was in my bathrobe and curlers.
我当时在浴袍和卷发器中。
wǒ   dāng   shí   zài   yù   páo   hé   juǎn   fā   qì   zhōng

321
00:23:42,589 --> 00:23:45,175
Aren't you going to change? You're on soon.
你不会改变吗？你很快。
nǐ   bù   huì   gǎi   biàn   ma   nǐ   hěn   kuài

322
00:23:49,263 --> 00:23:51,223
How did he know where you live?
他怎么知道你住在哪里？
tā   zěn   me   zhī   dào   nǐ   zhù   zài   nǎ   lǐ

323
00:23:51,390 --> 00:23:54,393
Good question. You must have told him.
好问题。你一定已经告诉他。
hǎo   wèn   tí   nǐ   yī   dìng   yǐ   jīng   gào   sù   tā

324
00:23:54,601 --> 00:23:56,270
I never told him.
我从未告诉过他。
wǒ   cóng   wèi   gào   sù   guò   tā

325
00:23:56,436 --> 00:23:59,064
Well, I certainly didn't tell him.
好吧，我当然没有告诉他。
hǎo   ba   wǒ   dāng   rán   méi   yǒu   gào   sù   tā

326
00:23:59,231 --> 00:24:02,276
I don't like people knowing where I live.
我不喜欢人们知道我住在哪里。
wǒ   bù   xǐ   huān   rén   men   zhī   dào   wǒ   zhù   zài   nǎ   lǐ

327
00:24:02,484 --> 00:24:06,196
Speaking of which, I really can't stay there any longer.
说到这，我真的不能再呆在那里了。
shuō   dào   zhè   wǒ   zhēn   de   bù   néng   zài   dāi   zài   nà   lǐ   le

328
00:24:06,363 --> 00:24:10,242
Mind if I stay with you until I find another room?
介意我是否和你在一起，直到找到另一个房间？
jiè   yì   wǒ   shì   fǒu   hé   nǐ   zài   yī   qǐ   zhí   dào   zhǎo   dào   lìng   yī   gè   fáng   jiān

329
00:24:10,576 --> 00:24:13,412
Of course not. I've told you many times.
当然不是。我已经告诉过你很多次。
dāng   rán   bù   shì   wǒ   yǐ   jīng   gào   sù   guò   nǐ   hěn   duō   cì

330
00:24:13,579 --> 00:24:15,289
You're a sweetheart.
你是一个甜心。
nǐ   shì   yī   gè   tián   xīn

331
00:24:20,502 --> 00:24:22,629
- What are you looking for? - A cigarette.
- 你要买什么？ - 香烟。
nǐ   yào   mǎi   shén   me   xiāng   yān

332
00:24:23,172 --> 00:24:25,132
- I'll get you one. - Fine!
- 我给你一个。 - 美好的！
wǒ   gěi   nǐ   yī   gè   měi   hǎo   de

333
00:24:26,925 --> 00:24:28,302
Thanks.
谢谢。
xiè   xiè

334
00:24:28,802 --> 00:24:30,512
- When did he come by? - Who?
- 他什么时候来的？ - WHO？
tā   shén   me   shí   hòu   lái   de

335
00:24:30,679 --> 00:24:32,139
Giorgio.
乔治。
qiáo   zhì

336
00:24:32,514 --> 00:24:34,850
Early this morning. I was getting dressed.
今天清晨。我穿衣服。
jīn   tiān   qīng   chén   wǒ   chuān   yī   fú

337
00:24:35,350 --> 00:24:37,352
<i>Miss Mari, you're on.</i>
<i>玛丽小姐，你在。</i>
mǎ   lì   xiǎo   jiě   nǐ   zài

338
00:24:38,103 --> 00:24:40,981
I don't understand. Are you in love with him or not?
我不明白。你是否爱上了他？
wǒ   bù   míng   bái   nǐ   shì   fǒu   ài   shàng   le   tā

339
00:24:41,190 --> 00:24:43,442
He's nice, I'll give you that.
他很好，我给你。
tā   hěn   hǎo   wǒ   gěi   nǐ

340
00:24:43,609 --> 00:24:45,861
Would you kindly stay out of it?
您会待在它的情况下吗？
nín   huì   dài   zài   tā   de   qíng   kuàng   xià   ma

341
00:24:46,028 --> 00:24:48,155
It's nothing to me, as long as you're happy.
只要您快乐，这对我来说是什么。
zhǐ   yào   nín   kuài   lè   zhè   duì   wǒ   lái   shuō   shì   shén   me

342
00:24:49,573 --> 00:24:51,200
You feel sick?
你感到恶心吗？
nǐ   gǎn   dào   è   xīn   ma

343
00:24:51,742 --> 00:24:53,327
No, it's nothing.
不，没什么。
bù   méi   shén   me

344
00:24:53,535 --> 00:24:57,414
Marina... again? You know it's bad for you.
码头...再次？你知道这对你不利。
mǎ   tóu   zài   cì   nǐ   zhī   dào   zhè   duì   nǐ   bù   lì

345
00:24:57,581 --> 00:24:58,999
That's stupid.
那很愚蠢。
nà   hěn   yú   chǔn

346
00:24:59,208 --> 00:25:03,128
Lots of things are bad for us, but we do them anyway.
很多事情对我们有害，但无论如何我们都会做。
hěn   duō   shì   qíng   duì   wǒ   men   yǒu   hài   dàn   wú   lùn   rú   hé   wǒ   men   dōu   huì   zuò

347
00:25:04,838 --> 00:25:06,298
I'm coming.
我要来。
wǒ   yào   lái

348
00:25:09,510 --> 00:25:11,845
Good evening. How are you?
晚上好。你好吗？
wǎn   shàng   hǎo   nǐ   hǎo   ma

349
00:25:12,012 --> 00:25:14,473
Fine, and you? How beautiful you look tonight!
很好，你呢？你今晚看起来多么美丽！
hěn   hǎo   nǐ   ne   nǐ   jīn   wǎn   kàn   qǐ   lái   duō   me   měi   lì

350
00:25:14,681 --> 00:25:16,391
But you're always so chic.
但是你总是很时尚。
dàn   shì   nǐ   zǒng   shì   hěn   shí   shàng

351
00:25:16,558 --> 00:25:18,977
- I'll be going. - Ah, Laura.
- 我要去。 - 啊，劳拉。
wǒ   yào   qù   a   láo   lā

352
00:25:19,144 --> 00:25:22,147
Try and hurry, or the boss will be mad.
尝试快点，否则老板会生气。
cháng   shì   kuài   diǎn   fǒu   zé   lǎo   bǎn   huì   shēng   qì

353
00:25:22,314 --> 00:25:24,608
- I have to go. - Yes, dear.
- 我得走了。 - 是的亲爱的。
wǒ   dé   zǒu   le   shì   de   qīn   ài   de

354
00:25:25,776 --> 00:25:27,402
Did you find some?
你找到了吗？
nǐ   zhǎo   dào   le   ma

355
00:25:27,694 --> 00:25:29,363
You're a darling!
你是亲爱的！
nǐ   shì   qīn   ài   de

356
00:25:44,586 --> 00:25:47,714
He has no schedule anymore - always in and out.
他没有时间表 - 总是进出。
tā   méi   yǒu   shí   jiān   biǎo   zǒng   shì   jìn   chū

357
00:25:47,881 --> 00:25:51,927
And these days, when you shouldn't even stick your nose out the window.
这些天，当您甚至不应该将鼻子伸出窗户时。
zhè   xiē   tiān   dāng   nín   shèn   zhì   bù   yīng   gāi   jiāng   bí   zi   shēn   chū   chuāng   hù   shí

358
00:25:52,302 --> 00:25:53,720
He's always out and about.
他总是在外面。
tā   zǒng   shì   zài   wài   miàn

359
00:25:53,887 --> 00:25:56,890
- He must have a good reason. - Let's hope so.
- 他必须有充分的理由。 - 希望这样。
tā   bì   xū   yǒu   chōng   fēn   de   lǐ   yóu   xī   wàng   zhè   yàng

360
00:25:57,057 --> 00:25:58,725
Agostino, I'm surprised at you.
阿戈斯蒂诺，我对你感到惊讶。
ā   gē   sī   dì   nuò   wǒ   duì   nǐ   gǎn   dào   jīng   yà

361
00:25:58,892 --> 00:26:00,227
Come now.
现在来。
xiàn   zài   lái

362
00:26:00,394 --> 00:26:05,399
You think I don't know you were behind that hubbub at the bakery today?
您认为我不知道您今天在面包店里落后于那个Hubbub吗？
nín   rèn   wèi   wǒ   bù   zhī   dào   nín   jīn   tiān   zài   miàn   bāo   diàn   lǐ   luò   hòu   yú   nà   gè   ma

363
00:26:05,607 --> 00:26:07,234
- Me? - Yes!
- 我？ - 是的！
wǒ   shì   de

364
00:26:07,442 --> 00:26:10,779
You think I'm an idiot? I know all about it.
你以为我是个白痴吗？我知道这一切。
nǐ   yǐ   wèi   wǒ   shì   gè   bái   chī   ma   wǒ   zhī   dào   zhè   yī   qiè

365
00:26:10,946 --> 00:26:14,116
And if you keep up these antics, you're all headed for trouble.
而且，如果您保持这些滑稽动作，那么您都会遇到麻烦。
ér   qiě   rú   guǒ   nín   bǎo   chí   zhè   xiē   huá   jī   dòng   zuò   nà   me   nín   dōu   huì   yù   dào   má   fán

366
00:26:14,283 --> 00:26:16,660
- Let's hope not. - Yes, let's.
- 希望不要。 - 是的，让我们吧。
xī   wàng   bù   yào   shì   de   ràng   wǒ   men   ba

367
00:26:17,327 --> 00:26:19,872
Cabbage soup. - I can tell.
卷心菜汤。 - 我可以说。
juǎn   xīn   cài   tāng   wǒ   kě   yǐ   shuō

368
00:26:20,080 --> 00:26:22,040
What time is it? The curfew's at 5:00.
现在是几奌？宵禁在5:00。
xiàn   zài   shì   jǐ   diǎn   xiāo   jìn   zài

369
00:26:22,207 --> 00:26:24,418
Let's see. It's 4:30.
让我们来看看。是4:30。
ràng   wǒ   men   lái   kàn   kàn   shì

370
00:26:24,585 --> 00:26:27,337
- I better be going. - You want to leave a message?
- 我最好去。 - 您想留言吗？
wǒ   zuì   hǎo   qù   nín   xiǎng   liú   yán   ma

371
00:26:27,504 --> 00:26:29,882
I wanted to talk to Don Pietro,
我想和唐·皮特罗（Don Pietro）交谈
wǒ   xiǎng   hé   táng   pí   tè   luó   jiāo   tán

372
00:26:30,048 --> 00:26:32,509
but I'll do it tomorrow before the wedding.
但是我明天在婚礼前做。
dàn   shì   wǒ   míng   tiān   zài   hūn   lǐ   qián   zuò

373
00:26:32,676 --> 00:26:34,136
Ah, finally.
啊，终于。
a   zhōng   yú

374
00:26:35,179 --> 00:26:37,806
Good evening, Don Pietro.
晚上好，唐·彼得罗。
wǎn   shàng   hǎo   táng   bǐ   dé   luó

375
00:26:41,018 --> 00:26:44,313
I've told you not to cook on the heater.
我告诉过你不要在加热器上做饭。
wǒ   gào   sù   guò   nǐ   bù   yào   zài   jiā   rè   qì   shàng   zuò   fàn

376
00:26:45,230 --> 00:26:46,857
And cabbage, no less.
和白菜，不少。
hé   bái   cài   bù   shǎo

377
00:26:48,025 --> 00:26:50,235
Agostino, don't answer back.
阿戈斯蒂诺，不要回答。
ā   gē   sī   dì   nuò   bù   yào   huí   dá

378
00:26:50,402 --> 00:26:53,906
- It's either the stove or the heater. - Fine.
- 它是炉子或加热器。 - 美好的。
tā   shì   lú   zi   huò   jiā   rè   qì   měi   hǎo   de

379
00:26:55,449 --> 00:26:59,620
More books! No money for food, and you keep buying books.
更多书！没有钱来买书，您会继续购买书籍。
gèng   duō   shū   méi   yǒu   qián   lái   mǎi   shū   nín   huì   jì   xù   gòu   mǎi   shū   jí

380
00:26:59,786 --> 00:27:02,414
Hands off. I'm taking them to San Lorenzo.
放开。我将他们带到圣洛伦佐。
fàng   kāi   wǒ   jiāng   tā   men   dài   dào   shèng   luò   lún   zuǒ

381
00:27:02,581 --> 00:27:05,792
You're going out again? The curfew's in 20 minutes.
你再出去吗？宵禁在20分钟内。
nǐ   zài   chū   qù   ma   xiāo   jìn   zài   fēn   zhōng   nèi

382
00:27:05,959 --> 00:27:09,004
It doesn't matter. Doctors and priests can still be out.
没关系。医生和祭司仍然可以出去。
méi   guān   xì   yī   shēng   hé   jì   sī   réng   rán   kě   yǐ   chū   qù

383
00:27:09,171 --> 00:27:11,673
- And midwives too. - What?
- 和助产士。 - 什么？
hé   zhù   chǎn   shì   shén   me

384
00:27:11,840 --> 00:27:13,467
I read it on the posters.
我在海报上读了它。
wǒ   zài   hǎi   bào   shàng   dú   le   tā

385
00:27:13,675 --> 00:27:16,845
But you could get shot in the dark with these thugs around.
但是，您可能会在黑暗中被这些暴徒在黑暗中被枪杀。
dàn   shì   nín   kě   néng   huì   zài   hēi   àn   zhōng   bèi   zhè   xiē   bào   tú   zài   hēi   àn   zhōng   bèi   qiāng   shā

386
00:27:17,012 --> 00:27:21,141
Don Pietro, I came... for confession.
唐·彼得罗（Don Pietro），我来了...供认。
táng   bǐ   dé   luó   wǒ   lái   le   gōng   rèn

387
00:27:21,350 --> 00:27:24,603
I have to go out. Maybe tomorrow morning?
我必须出去。也许明天早上？
wǒ   bì   xū   chū   qù   yě   xǔ   míng   tiān   zǎo   shàng

388
00:27:24,770 --> 00:27:28,148
Fine. I'll walk with you a ways now.
美好的。我现在和你一起走。
měi   hǎo   de   wǒ   xiàn   zài   hé   nǐ   yī   qǐ   zǒu

389
00:27:29,191 --> 00:27:30,651
Let me carry your package.
让我携带你的包裹。
ràng   wǒ   xié   dài   nǐ   de   bāo   guǒ

390
00:27:30,817 --> 00:27:34,029
We can't have a priest carrying a package.
我们不能有一个携带包裹的牧师。
wǒ   men   bù   néng   yǒu   yī   gè   xié   dài   bāo   guǒ   de   mù   shī

391
00:27:34,196 --> 00:27:37,241
Besides, I'm already carrying so much.
此外，我已经携带了很多。
cǐ   wài   wǒ   yǐ   jīng   xié   dài   le   hěn   duō

392
00:27:37,407 --> 00:27:39,743
Come on, it's getting late.
来吧，已经很晚了。
lái   ba   yǐ   jīng   hěn   wǎn   le

393
00:27:39,910 --> 00:27:42,246
Bye, Agostino. - And stop worrying.
再见，阿戈斯蒂诺。 - 不再担心。
zài   jiàn   ā   gē   sī   dì   nuò   bù   zài   dān   xīn

394
00:27:42,412 --> 00:27:44,957
If this war isn't over soon, I'll go crazy!
如果这场战争还没有结束，我会发疯！
rú   guǒ   zhè   chǎng   zhàn   zhēng   hái   méi   yǒu   jié   shù   wǒ   huì   fā   fēng

395
00:28:02,266 --> 00:28:06,061
Are you the priest here? Don Pietro Pellegrini?
你是牧师吗？ Don Pietro Pellegrini？
nǐ   shì   mù   shī   ma

396
00:28:06,228 --> 00:28:08,146
I'd like to speak to you.
我想和你说话。
wǒ   xiǎng   hé   nǐ   shuō   huà

397
00:28:10,399 --> 00:28:11,984
Please...
请...
qǐng

398
00:28:12,734 --> 00:28:15,445
I'll be going. Here's your package.
我要去的。这是你的包裹。
wǒ   yào   qù   de   zhè   shì   nǐ   de   bāo   guǒ

399
00:28:15,904 --> 00:28:18,240
I wonder what he wants. - Who knows?
我想知道他想要什么。 - 谁知道？
wǒ   xiǎng   zhī   dào   tā   xiǎng   yào   shén   me   shuí   zhī   dào

400
00:28:20,033 --> 00:28:22,202
Perhaps you should...
也许你应该...
yě   xǔ   nǐ   yīng   gāi

401
00:28:23,704 --> 00:28:25,747
wait for me over there.
在那边等我。
zài   nà   biān   děng   wǒ

402
00:28:40,679 --> 00:28:42,139
Have a seat.
有座位。
yǒu   zuò   wèi

403
00:28:43,432 --> 00:28:45,225
Step outside a moment.
走一会儿。
zǒu   yī   huì   ér

404
00:28:48,061 --> 00:28:49,521
Please.
请。
qǐng

405
00:28:51,857 --> 00:28:53,734
What is it?
这是什么？
zhè   shì   shén   me

406
00:29:12,669 --> 00:29:15,547
From Don Saverio Derisi,
来自Don Saverio Derisi，
lái   zì

407
00:29:15,714 --> 00:29:17,674
the priest in Minturno.
Minturno的牧师。
de   mù   shī

408
00:29:30,938 --> 00:29:33,815
You mustn't think I'm a coward.
你一定不能认为我是胆小鬼。
nǐ   yī   dìng   bù   néng   rèn   wèi   wǒ   shì   dǎn   xiǎo   guǐ

409
00:29:34,900 --> 00:29:36,318
I can't take any more!
我不能再走了！
wǒ   bù   néng   zài   zǒu   le

410
00:29:42,574 --> 00:29:45,953
Don't lose heart. I'll try to help you.
不要灰心。我会尽力帮助您。
bù   yào   huī   xīn   wǒ   huì   jǐn   lì   bāng   zhù   nín

411
00:29:47,621 --> 00:29:49,414
Where have you come from?
你来自哪里？
nǐ   lái   zì   nǎ   lǐ

412
00:29:50,123 --> 00:29:53,418
Cassino. It's a living hell there!
卡西诺。那里是一个活着的地狱！
kǎ   xī   nuò   nà   lǐ   shì   yī   gè   huó   zhe   de   dì   yù

413
00:30:02,177 --> 00:30:04,596
What did he want? No, I'll carry it.
他想要什么？不，我会随身携带。
tā   xiǎng   yào   shén   me   bù   wǒ   huì   suí   shēn   xié   dài

414
00:30:04,763 --> 00:30:06,723
He wanted information.
他想要信息。
tā   xiǎng   yào   xìn   xī

415
00:30:06,890 --> 00:30:09,393
Just the sight of those guys and I -
只是那些家伙的景象 -
zhǐ   shì   nà   xiē   jiā   huǒ   de   jǐng   xiàng

416
00:30:11,270 --> 00:30:14,982
My last confession was so long ago that I'm almost ashamed.
我的最后一个认罪是很久以前，我几乎是ham愧的。
wǒ   de   zuì   hòu   yī   gè   rèn   zuì   shì   hěn   jiǔ   yǐ   qián   wǒ   jǐ   hū   shì   kuì   de

417
00:30:15,148 --> 00:30:17,109
No, let me talk.
不，让我谈谈。
bù   ràng   wǒ   tán   tán

418
00:30:17,568 --> 00:30:21,655
I've led a bad life. I've done so much I shouldn't have.
我过着糟糕的生活。我做了很多事情，我不应该做。
wǒ   guò   zhe   zāo   gāo   de   shēng   huó   wǒ   zuò   le   hěn   duō   shì   qíng   wǒ   bù   yīng   gāi   zuò

419
00:30:22,072 --> 00:30:26,618
You think I'm not ashamed to be married in my condition?
您认为我不因结婚而感到羞耻吗？
nín   rèn   wèi   wǒ   bù   yīn   jié   hūn   ér   gǎn   dào   xiū   chǐ   ma

420
00:30:26,827 --> 00:30:29,079
But you'd never understand.
但是你永远不会理解。
dàn   shì   nǐ   yǒng   yuǎn   bù   huì   lǐ   jiě

421
00:30:29,246 --> 00:30:31,415
There are things you do without thinking,
有些事情你不思考，
yǒu   xiē   shì   qíng   nǐ   bù   sī   kǎo

422
00:30:31,582 --> 00:30:34,251
that don't feel like you're doing wrong.
那不觉得你做错了。
nà   bù   jué   dé   nǐ   zuò   cuò   le

423
00:30:34,418 --> 00:30:35,961
I was so in love,
我是如此恋爱，
wǒ   shì   rú   cǐ   liàn   ài

424
00:30:36,170 --> 00:30:39,089
and he was so good, so decent.
他是如此的好，如此体面。
tā   shì   rú   cǐ   de   hǎo   rú   cǐ   tǐ   miàn

425
00:30:39,590 --> 00:30:43,135
I know he could have found someone better,
我知道他可以找到更好的人
wǒ   zhī   dào   tā   kě   yǐ   zhǎo   dào   gèng   hǎo   de   rén

426
00:30:43,302 --> 00:30:45,053
a young girl,
一个年轻的女孩，
yī   gè   nián   qīng   de   nǚ   hái

427
00:30:45,220 --> 00:30:48,724
not a penniless widow with a child
没有孩子的寡妇一文不见
méi   yǒu   hái   zi   de   guǎ   fù   yī   wén   bù   jiàn

428
00:30:48,891 --> 00:30:52,227
who had to sell everything just to get by.
谁不得不卖掉一切只是为由。
shuí   bù   dé   bù   mài   diào   yī   qiè   zhǐ   shì   wèi   yóu

429
00:30:52,394 --> 00:30:54,479
And life just keeps getting harder.
生活一直在越来越艰难。
shēng   huó   yī   zhí   zài   yuè   lái   yuè   jiān   nán

430
00:30:55,606 --> 00:31:01,236
How will we ever forget all this suffering, anxiety, and fear?
我们如何忘记所有这些痛苦，焦虑和恐惧？
wǒ   men   rú   hé   wàng   jì   suǒ   yǒu   zhè   xiē   tòng   kǔ   jiāo   lǜ   hé   kǒng   jù

431
00:31:02,321 --> 00:31:04,573
Doesn't Christ see us?
基督不见我们吗？
jī   dū   bù   jiàn   wǒ   men   ma

432
00:31:06,742 --> 00:31:10,871
So many people ask me that: "Doesn't Christ see us?"
这么多人问我：“基督不见我们吗？”
zhè   me   duō   rén   wèn   wǒ   jī   dū   bù   jiàn   wǒ   men   ma

433
00:31:11,038 --> 00:31:13,957
But are we sure we haven't deserved this scourge?
但是我们确定我们没有应有的祸害吗？
dàn   shì   wǒ   men   què   dìng   wǒ   men   méi   yǒu   yīng   yǒu   de   huò   hài   ma

434
00:31:14,124 --> 00:31:18,712
Are we sure we've always lived according to the Lord's laws?
我们确定我们一直按照主的法律生活吗？
wǒ   men   què   dìng   wǒ   men   yī   zhí   àn   zhào   zhǔ   de   fǎ   lǜ   shēng   huó   ma

435
00:31:19,713 --> 00:31:22,341
People never think of changing their ways,
人们永远不会想改变自己的方式，
rén   men   yǒng   yuǎn   bù   huì   xiǎng   gǎi   biàn   zì   jǐ   de   fāng   shì

436
00:31:22,508 --> 00:31:25,928
but when the piper must be paid, they despair and ask,
但是当必须付吹笛者时，他们绝望地问，
dàn   shì   dāng   bì   xū   fù   chuī   dí   zhě   shí   tā   men   jué   wàng   dì   wèn

437
00:31:26,094 --> 00:31:30,057
"Doesn't the Lord see us? Doesn't he take pity on us?"
“耶和华不见我们吗？他不怜悯我们吗？”
yé   hé   huá   bù   jiàn   wǒ   men   ma   tā   bù   lián   mǐn   wǒ   men   ma

438
00:31:30,516 --> 00:31:32,684
Yes, he does,
是的，他确实
shì   de   tā   què   shí

439
00:31:32,851 --> 00:31:36,313
but we have so much to be forgiven for,
但是我们有很多宽恕，
dàn   shì   wǒ   men   yǒu   hěn   duō   kuān   shù

440
00:31:36,522 --> 00:31:39,858
and for that we must pray and forgive many things.
为此，我们必须祈祷并原谅许多事情。
wèi   cǐ   wǒ   men   bì   xū   qí   dǎo   bìng   yuán   liàng   xǔ   duō   shì   qíng

441
00:31:40,025 --> 00:31:43,362
You're right, but how do we forgive?
你是对的，但是我们如何原谅？
nǐ   shì   duì   de   dàn   shì   wǒ   men   rú   hé   yuán   liàng

442
00:31:43,529 --> 00:31:47,741
I see those guys and I want to smash their faces in.
我看到那些家伙，我想砸他们的脸。
wǒ   kàn   dào   nà   xiē   jiā   huǒ   wǒ   xiǎng   zá   tā   men   de   liǎn

443
00:31:47,950 --> 00:31:51,328
You're right. I mean... give me that package.
你说得对。我的意思是...给我那个包裹。
nǐ   shuō   dé   duì   wǒ   de   yì   sī   shì   gěi   wǒ   nà   gè   bāo   guǒ

444
00:31:51,495 --> 00:31:54,832
It's getting late. Good-bye, Pina.
已经晚了。再见，皮纳。
yǐ   jīng   wǎn   le   zài   jiàn   pí   nà

445
00:32:32,619 --> 00:32:34,454
She came looking for help.
她来找帮助。
tā   lái   zhǎo   bāng   zhù

446
00:32:34,621 --> 00:32:37,124
The Gestapo had hauled in her fiance.
Gestapo在未婚夫中拖了。
zài   wèi   hūn   fū   zhōng   tuō   le

447
00:32:37,332 --> 00:32:39,710
"Don't worry. I'll take care of it," I told her.
“不用担心。我会照顾的，”我告诉她。
bù   yòng   dān   xīn   wǒ   huì   zhào   gù   de   wǒ   gào   sù   tā

448
00:32:39,877 --> 00:32:42,504
What a pair of legs!
多腿！
duō   tuǐ

449
00:32:43,547 --> 00:32:45,549
Halt! Hands up!
停止！举起！
tíng   zhǐ   jǔ   qǐ

450
00:32:47,009 --> 00:32:48,677
I have a permit.
我有许可证。
wǒ   yǒu   xǔ   kě   zhèng

451
00:32:51,513 --> 00:32:53,140
Printer.
打印机。
dǎ   yìn   jī

452
00:32:54,516 --> 00:32:56,768
Says so right there.
就这么说。
jiù   zhè   me   shuō

453
00:32:57,769 --> 00:33:00,105
All right. Go home quickly.
好的。快速回家。
hǎo   de   kuài   sù   huí   jiā

454
00:33:26,882 --> 00:33:28,967
<i>Auf Wiedersehen, Captain, and thanks.</i>
<i>再见，上尉，谢谢。 </i>
zài   jiàn   shàng   wèi   xiè   xiè

455
00:33:29,134 --> 00:33:31,637
Good night. See you tomorrow - don't forget.
晚安。明天见 - 别忘了。
wǎn   ān   míng   tiān   jiàn   bié   wàng   le

456
00:33:39,394 --> 00:33:41,855
Francesco, you scared me.
弗朗切斯科，你害怕我。
fú   lǎng   qiè   sī   kē   nǐ   hài   pà   wǒ

457
00:33:42,940 --> 00:33:46,068
I'm a bit late. They insisted on seeing me home.
我有点晚。他们坚持见我回家。
wǒ   yǒu   diǎn   wǎn   tā   men   jiān   chí   jiàn   wǒ   huí   jiā

458
00:33:46,235 --> 00:33:48,529
Nothing wrong with that, is there?
没错，那里吗？
méi   cuò   nà   lǐ   ma

459
00:33:52,908 --> 00:33:54,535
Hi, Francesco.
嗨，弗朗切斯科。
hāi   fú   lǎng   qiè   sī   kē

460
00:33:55,661 --> 00:33:57,746
- You got away, eh? - This time at least,
- 你离开了，是吗？ - 至少这次，
nǐ   lí   kāi   le   shì   ma   zhì   shǎo   zhè   cì

461
00:33:57,913 --> 00:33:59,832
with the landlady and Nannina's help.
在房东和Nannina的帮助下。
zài   fáng   dōng   hé   de   bāng   zhù   xià

462
00:33:59,998 --> 00:34:02,709
You know they tore the place apart this morning?
你知道他们今天早上把这个地方撕裂了吗？
nǐ   zhī   dào   tā   men   jīn   tiān   zǎo   shàng   bǎ   zhè   gè   dì   fāng   sī   liè   le   ma

463
00:34:02,918 --> 00:34:04,878
A waste of time. There was nothing there.
浪费时间。那里什么都没有。
làng   fèi   shí   jiān   nà   lǐ   shén   me   dōu   méi   yǒu

464
00:34:05,045 --> 00:34:08,173
- Pina let you in? - Yes, she was very kind.
- 皮纳让你进去吗？ - 是的，她很友善。
pí   nà   ràng   nǐ   jìn   qù   ma   shì   de   tā   hěn   yǒu   shàn

465
00:34:08,340 --> 00:34:11,218
- What do you think? - You're smart to marry her.
- 你怎么认为？ - 你很聪明地嫁给她。
nǐ   zěn   me   rèn   wèi   nǐ   hěn   cōng   míng   dì   jià   gěi   tā

466
00:34:11,385 --> 00:34:14,429
At first she took me for a cop and gave me hell.
起初，她带我去了一个警察，给了我地狱。
qǐ   chū   tā   dài   wǒ   qù   le   yī   gè   jǐng   chá   gěi   le   wǒ   dì   yù

467
00:34:14,596 --> 00:34:16,390
I can imagine.
我可以想象。
wǒ   kě   yǐ   xiǎng   xiàng

468
00:34:16,598 --> 00:34:19,935
Did you know Don Pietro met Gino? - Really? I'm glad.
你知道唐·彼得罗遇见了吉诺吗？ - 真的吗？我很高兴。
nǐ   zhī   dào   táng   bǐ   dé   luó   yù   jiàn   le   jí   nuò   ma   zhēn   de   ma   wǒ   hěn   gāo   xīng

469
00:34:20,102 --> 00:34:21,687
What did he say about my matter?
他对我的问题说了什么？
tā   duì   wǒ   de   wèn   tí   shuō   le   shén   me

470
00:34:21,895 --> 00:34:23,814
He's worried. You were to meet the old man today.
他很担心。你今天要见老人。
tā   hěn   dān   xīn   nǐ   jīn   tiān   yào   jiàn   lǎo   rén

471
00:34:23,981 --> 00:34:27,276
- When did he get in? - Last night. But you can't see him.
- 他什么时候进来的？ - 昨夜。但是你看不到他。
tā   shén   me   shí   hòu   jìn   lái   de   zuó   yè   dàn   shì   nǐ   kàn   bù   dào   tā

472
00:34:27,442 --> 00:34:31,446
Gino says you have to drop all contact with central for a while.
吉诺（Gino）说，您必须将所有与Central的接触都放置一段时间。
jí   nuò   shuō   nín   bì   xū   jiāng   suǒ   yǒu   yǔ   de   jiē   chù   dōu   fàng   zhì   yī   duàn   shí   jiān

473
00:34:32,030 --> 00:34:35,284
True, but to stop short after months of work!
是的，但是几个月后就停止了！
shì   de   dàn   shì   jǐ   gè   yuè   hòu   jiù   tíng   zhǐ   le

474
00:34:35,450 --> 00:34:40,080
How'd they catch on to me? We have to find out what they know.
他们如何抓住我？我们必须找出他们所知道的。
tā   men   rú   hé   zhuā   zhù   wǒ   wǒ   men   bì   xū   zhǎo   chū   tā   men   suǒ   zhī   dào   de

475
00:34:40,289 --> 00:34:43,709
We'll try, but it won't be easy with the Gestapo.
我们会尝试的，但是盖世太保并不容易。
wǒ   men   huì   cháng   shì   de   dàn   shì   gài   shì   tài   bǎo   bìng   bù   róng   yì

476
00:34:43,876 --> 00:34:46,378
If it was the Italian police -
如果是意大利警察 -
rú   guǒ   shì   yì   dà   lì   jǐng   chá

477
00:34:46,837 --> 00:34:49,756
Let's hope Don Pietro met our friend from Tagliacozzo.
希望唐·彼得罗（Don Pietro）从塔格利亚科佐（Tagliacozzo）认识了我们的朋友。
xī   wàng   táng   bǐ   dé   luó   cóng   tǎ   gé   lì   yà   kē   zuǒ   rèn   shí   le   wǒ   men   de   péng   yǒu

478
00:34:49,923 --> 00:34:51,800
Let's hope so.
希望如此。
xī   wàng   rú   cǐ

479
00:34:55,470 --> 00:34:57,556
Ah, I brought you our newspaper.
啊，我给你带来了我们的报纸。
a   wǒ   gěi   nǐ   dài   lái   le   wǒ   men   de   bào   zhǐ

480
00:35:00,142 --> 00:35:01,894
Came out all right, didn't it?
出来了，不是吗？
chū   lái   le   bù   shì   ma

481
00:35:02,311 --> 00:35:03,937
How many copies?
多少份？
duō   shǎo   fèn

482
00:35:04,104 --> 00:35:05,647
Twelve thousand.
十二千。
shí   èr   qiān

483
00:35:07,649 --> 00:35:09,276
That's Pina.
那是皮纳。
nà   shì   pí   nà

484
00:35:13,405 --> 00:35:15,032
Hi. How are you?
你好。你好吗？
nǐ   hǎo   nǐ   hǎo   ma

485
00:35:15,324 --> 00:35:17,618
I'm worried about Marcello. He's disappeared.
我担心马塞洛。他消失了。
wǒ   dān   xīn   mǎ   sāi   luò   tā   xiāo   shī   le

486
00:35:17,784 --> 00:35:20,329
I've searched the whole building.
我已经搜索了整个建筑物。
wǒ   yǐ   jīng   sōu   suǒ   le   zhěng   gè   jiàn   zhù   wù

487
00:35:20,496 --> 00:35:22,706
- He's probably at Romoletto's. - He's not.
- 他可能在Romoletto的。 - 他不是。
tā   kě   néng   zài   de   tā   bù   shì

488
00:35:22,873 --> 00:35:25,292
And two other boys are missing too.
另外两个男孩也失踪了。
lìng   wài   liǎng   gè   nán   hái   yě   shī   zōng   le

489
00:35:25,501 --> 00:35:27,169
Where could they have gone?
他们可以去哪里？
tā   men   kě   yǐ   qù   nǎ   lǐ

490
00:35:27,336 --> 00:35:30,297
- I'm afraid they've gone out. - After curfew?
- 恐怕他们出去了。 - 宵禁之后？
kǒng   pà   tā   men   chū   qù   le   xiāo   jìn   zhī   hòu

491
00:36:07,793 --> 00:36:10,212
Well done. I'm proud of you.
做得好。我为你感到骄傲。
zuò   dé   hǎo   wǒ   wèi   nǐ   gǎn   dào   jiāo   ào

492
00:36:12,714 --> 00:36:14,508
Let's step on it, boys.
让我们踩一下，男孩。
ràng   wǒ   men   cǎi   yī   xià   nán   hái

493
00:36:17,594 --> 00:36:19,638
Let's wait for Otello.
让我们等待Otello。
ràng   wǒ   men   děng   dài

494
00:36:31,400 --> 00:36:33,026
Good night.
晚安。
wǎn   ān

495
00:36:38,407 --> 00:36:42,327
<i>So you're still alive! Well, I'll kill you now!</i>
<i>所以你还活着！好吧，我现在杀了你！</i>
suǒ   yǐ   nǐ   hái   huó   zhe   hǎo   ba   wǒ   xiàn   zài   shā   le   nǐ

496
00:36:43,787 --> 00:36:46,999
If I had a father like that, I'd show him.
如果我有这样的父亲，我会告诉他。
rú   guǒ   wǒ   yǒu   zhè   yàng   de   fù   qīn   wǒ   huì   gào   sù   tā

497
00:36:47,166 --> 00:36:48,667
Good night.
晚安。
wǎn   ān

498
00:36:51,253 --> 00:36:54,423
You little devil! Coming home at this hour!
你小魔鬼！这个小时回家！
nǐ   xiǎo   mó   guǐ   zhè   gè   xiǎo   shí   huí   jiā

499
00:37:02,931 --> 00:37:05,225
We'd better go in one at a time.
我们最好一次参加。
wǒ   men   zuì   hǎo   yī   cì   cān   jiā

500
00:37:05,392 --> 00:37:07,019
You're right. You go first.
你说得对。你先去。
nǐ   shuō   dé   duì   nǐ   xiān   qù

501
00:37:07,186 --> 00:37:08,562
<i>You little monsters!</i>
<i>你小怪物！</i>
nǐ   xiǎo   guài   wù

502
00:37:08,770 --> 00:37:09,438
They're back.
他们回来了。
tā   men   huí   lái   le

503
00:37:09,605 --> 00:37:10,689
Trouble-maker!
麻烦制造者！
má   fán   zhì   zào   zhě

504
00:37:10,856 --> 00:37:14,693
I'll tan your hide! Give me heart failure, will you?
我会晒黑你的皮！给我心力衰竭，对吗？
wǒ   huì   shài   hēi   nǐ   de   pí   gěi   wǒ   xīn   lì   shuāi   jié   duì   ma

505
00:37:16,445 --> 00:37:18,822
I'm going over for a minute or there'll be murder.
我要去一分钟，否则会谋杀。
wǒ   yào   qù   yī   fēn   zhōng   fǒu   zé   huì   móu   shā

506
00:37:19,114 --> 00:37:21,116
- Look how they look! - Where were you?
- 看看他们的外观！ - 当时你在哪里？
kàn   kàn   tā   men   de   wài   guān   dāng   shí   nǐ   zài   nǎ   lǐ

507
00:37:21,283 --> 00:37:22,910
- At Romoletto's. - No, you weren't!
- 在Romoletto's。 - 不，你不是！
zài   bù   nǐ   bù   shì

508
00:37:23,118 --> 00:37:25,078
- We were downstairs. - Where?
- 我们在楼下。 - 在哪里？
wǒ   men   zài   lóu   xià   zài   nǎ   lǐ

509
00:37:25,287 --> 00:37:27,998
- Can't you see they're lying? - I'll kill him!
- 你看不到他们在说谎吗？ - 我会杀了他！
nǐ   kàn   bù   dào   tā   men   zài   shuō   huǎng   ma   wǒ   huì   shā   le   tā

510
00:37:28,165 --> 00:37:30,667
No, I'll slap 'em silly!
不，我很傻！
bù   wǒ   hěn   shǎ

511
00:37:30,834 --> 00:37:33,378
Get to bed, you two.
你们两个上床睡觉。
nǐ   men   liǎng   gè   shàng   chuáng   shuì   jué

512
00:37:33,545 --> 00:37:36,381
Calm down. - I've had it with them!
冷静下来。 - 我和他们在一起！
lěng   jìng   xià   lái   wǒ   hé   tā   men   zài   yī   qǐ

513
00:37:36,548 --> 00:37:38,050
They're just kids.
他们只是孩子。
tā   men   zhǐ   shì   hái   zi

514
00:37:38,592 --> 00:37:43,305
I can't get a moment's peace here! I work all day!
我不能在这里得到片刻的和平！我整天工作！
wǒ   bù   néng   zài   zhè   lǐ   dé   dào   piàn   kè   de   hé   píng   wǒ   zhěng   tiān   gōng   zuò

515
00:37:43,472 --> 00:37:44,765
Some work!
一些工作！
yī   xiē   gōng   zuò

516
00:37:44,932 --> 00:37:47,726
What was that? Speak clearly!
那是什么？说清楚！
nà   shì   shén   me   shuō   qīng   chǔ

517
00:37:47,893 --> 00:37:49,353
You'd better just go back to bed.
你最好回到床上。
nǐ   zuì   hǎo   huí   dào   chuáng   shàng

518
00:37:49,520 --> 00:37:52,314
Can't I talk in my own home?
我不能在自己家里说话吗？
wǒ   bù   néng   zài   zì   jǐ   jiā   lǐ   shuō   huà   ma

519
00:37:52,481 --> 00:37:54,399
This is my home. Go talk in your own room.
这是我的家。去你自己的房间里说话。
zhè   shì   wǒ   de   jiā   qù   nǐ   zì   jǐ   de   fáng   jiān   lǐ   shuō   huà

520
00:37:54,566 --> 00:37:57,653
We pay for kitchen privileges. - Laura, forget it.
我们支付厨房特权。 - 劳拉，算了。
wǒ   men   zhī   fù   chú   fáng   tè   quán   láo   lā   suàn   le

521
00:37:57,820 --> 00:38:00,072
Forget it? I'm fed up with living in this zoo!
忘了它？我厌倦了住在这个动物园里！
wàng   le   tā   wǒ   yàn   juàn   le   zhù   zài   zhè   gè   dòng   wù   yuán   lǐ

522
00:38:00,239 --> 00:38:01,782
Then get out!
然后出去！
rán   hòu   chū   qù

523
00:38:01,990 --> 00:38:06,829
Do you people have to fight every night?
你们每天晚上都必须战斗吗？
nǐ   men   měi   tiān   wǎn   shàng   dōu   bì   xū   zhàn   dòu   ma

524
00:38:07,538 --> 00:38:11,083
If she doesn't leave, one of these days I'll -
如果她不离开，这些日子之一我会 -
rú   guǒ   tā   bù   lí   kāi   zhè   xiē   rì   zi   zhī   yī   wǒ   huì

525
00:38:11,500 --> 00:38:14,127
Elide, is it ready yet?
Elide，准备好了吗？
zhǔn   bèi   hǎo   le   ma

526
00:38:14,628 --> 00:38:16,713
Oh! It's probably burned!
哦！它可能被烧毁了！
ó   tā   kě   néng   bèi   shāo   huǐ   le

527
00:38:16,880 --> 00:38:18,715
That little witch!
那个小巫婆！
nà   gè   xiǎo   wū   pó

528
00:38:19,132 --> 00:38:20,592
Come here.
来这里。
lái   zhè   lǐ

529
00:38:23,595 --> 00:38:25,222
It's a surprise.
这是一个惊喜。
zhè   shì   yī   gè   jīng   xǐ

530
00:38:25,389 --> 00:38:30,477
Elide's baking a cake for your wedding tomorrow.
Elide明天为您的婚礼烤蛋糕。
míng   tiān   wèi   nín   de   hūn   lǐ   kǎo   dàn   gāo

531
00:38:30,727 --> 00:38:34,982
I hope you two won't quarrel at the last minute,
希望你们两个不会在最后一刻吵架，
xī   wàng   nǐ   men   liǎng   gè   bù   huì   zài   zuì   hòu   yī   kè   chǎo   jià

532
00:38:35,148 --> 00:38:39,319
because we're going to have a real feast!
因为我们将举行一场真正的盛宴！
yīn   wèi   wǒ   men   jiāng   jǔ   xíng   yī   chǎng   zhēn   zhèng   de   shèng   yàn

533
00:38:41,446 --> 00:38:44,408
- That's his greatest worry. - Off to bed. Good night.
- 这是他最大的担忧。 - 上床。晚安。
zhè   shì   tā   zuì   dà   de   dān   yōu   shàng   chuáng   wǎn   ān

534
00:38:44,575 --> 00:38:46,994
Turn out the light, will ya?
熄灯，会吗？
xī   dēng   huì   ma

535
00:38:51,623 --> 00:38:53,458
We fixed 'em good, eh?
我们固定好了，是吗？
wǒ   men   gù   dìng   hǎo   le   shì   ma

536
00:38:53,625 --> 00:38:55,210
You never take me along.
你永远不会带我走。
nǐ   yǒng   yuǎn   bù   huì   dài   wǒ   zǒu

537
00:38:55,377 --> 00:38:56,753
You're a woman!
你是女人！
nǐ   shì   nǚ   rén

538
00:38:56,920 --> 00:38:59,756
So? Can't women be heroes too?
所以？女人也不能成为英雄吗？
suǒ   yǐ   nǚ   rén   yě   bù   néng   chéng   wèi   yīng   xióng   ma

539
00:38:59,923 --> 00:39:02,426
Sure, but Romoletto says
当然，但是Romoletto说
dāng   rán   dàn   shì   shuō

540
00:39:02,593 --> 00:39:05,554
that women always mean trouble.
那个女人总是在意义麻烦。
nà   gè   nǚ   rén   zǒng   shì   zài   yì   yì   má   fán

541
00:39:05,721 --> 00:39:07,055
You still awake?
你还醒了吗？
nǐ   hái   xǐng   le   ma

542
00:39:07,222 --> 00:39:08,724
Under the covers!
在封面下！
zài   fēng   miàn   xià

543
00:39:17,149 --> 00:39:18,609
Go to sleep.
睡觉。
shuì   jué

544
00:39:25,240 --> 00:39:26,825
Can't sleep?
不能睡觉？
bù   néng   shuì   jué

545
00:39:28,494 --> 00:39:29,953
I'm not sleepy.
我不是困了。
wǒ   bù   shì   kùn   le

546
00:39:31,038 --> 00:39:33,457
Where did you boys go with Romoletto?
你们男孩和Romoletto一起去哪里？
nǐ   men   nán   hái   hé   yī   qǐ   qù   nǎ   lǐ

547
00:39:33,624 --> 00:39:35,417
I can't tell you.
我不能告诉你。
wǒ   bù   néng   gào   sù   nǐ

548
00:39:35,584 --> 00:39:37,211
Not even me?
甚至不是我吗？
shèn   zhì   bù   shì   wǒ   ma

549
00:39:38,253 --> 00:39:40,380
No, it's a secret.
不，这是一个秘密。
bù   zhè   shì   yī   gè   mì   mì

550
00:39:41,632 --> 00:39:43,342
Then you're right.
那你是对的。
nà   nǐ   shì   duì   de

551
00:39:43,509 --> 00:39:45,469
You mustn't tell anyone.
你一定不能告诉任何人。
nǐ   yī   dìng   bù   néng   gào   sù   rèn   hé   rén

552
00:39:50,265 --> 00:39:51,808
Good night.
晚安。
wǎn   ān

553
00:39:56,188 --> 00:39:57,147
Hey...
嘿...
hēi

554
00:39:58,941 --> 00:40:00,442
What?
什么？
shén   me

555
00:40:02,444 --> 00:40:05,614
Do I really start calling you "papa" tomorrow?
明天我真的开始称呼您为“爸爸”吗？
míng   tiān   wǒ   zhēn   de   kāi   shǐ   chēng   hū   nín   wèi   bà   bà   ma

556
00:40:06,448 --> 00:40:07,574
If you want.
如果你想。
rú   guǒ   nǐ   xiǎng

557
00:40:07,783 --> 00:40:10,035
I do. I really like you.
我愿意。我真的很喜欢你。
wǒ   yuàn   yì   wǒ   zhēn   de   hěn   xǐ   huān   nǐ

558
00:40:21,797 --> 00:40:23,006
What's wrong?
怎么了？
zěn   me   le

559
00:40:23,799 --> 00:40:25,717
I had a fight with my sister.
我和姐姐打架。
wǒ   hé   jiě   jiě   dǎ   jià

560
00:40:25,884 --> 00:40:27,344
Again?
再次？
zài   cì

561
00:40:27,803 --> 00:40:29,721
She wants to leave.
她想离开。
tā   xiǎng   lí   kāi

562
00:40:29,888 --> 00:40:32,391
Says she won't even come to the wedding.
说她甚至不会参加婚礼。
shuō   tā   shèn   zhì   bù   huì   cān   jiā   hūn   lǐ

563
00:40:32,683 --> 00:40:34,643
That's just talk.
那只是说话。
nà   zhǐ   shì   shuō   huà

564
00:40:34,810 --> 00:40:38,438
No, she was serious. She's packing her bags.
不，她很认真。她打包了书包。
bù   tā   hěn   rèn   zhēn   tā   dǎ   bāo   le   shū   bāo

565
00:40:38,856 --> 00:40:41,149
She'll change her mind tomorrow.
她明天会改变主意。
tā   míng   tiān   huì   gǎi   biàn   zhǔ   yì

566
00:40:42,151 --> 00:40:44,069
I'm so tired!
我很累！
wǒ   hěn   lèi

567
00:40:44,236 --> 00:40:45,445
There now.
现在那里。
xiàn   zài   nà   lǐ

568
00:40:46,029 --> 00:40:47,614
I'm so tired!
我很累！
wǒ   hěn   lèi

569
00:40:47,823 --> 00:40:50,450
Go on and cry. Come in for a while.
继续哭泣。进来一会儿。
jì   xù   kū   qì   jìn   lái   yī   huì   ér

570
00:40:54,621 --> 00:40:57,583
- No, he's in there. - So? He's a friend.
- 不，他在那里。 - 所以？他是朋友。
bù   tā   zài   nà   lǐ   suǒ   yǐ   tā   shì   péng   yǒu

571
00:40:57,791 --> 00:41:01,378
I've wanted to talk with you alone for so long.
我想和你一个人聊天这么长时间。
wǒ   xiǎng   hé   nǐ   yī   gè   rén   liáo   tiān   zhè   me   zhǎng   shí   jiān

572
00:41:01,753 --> 00:41:02,963
Come here.
来这里。
lái   zhè   lǐ

573
00:41:04,173 --> 00:41:05,757
Let's sit down here,
让我们坐在这里，
ràng   wǒ   men   zuò   zài   zhè   lǐ

574
00:41:05,966 --> 00:41:09,678
like the very first time we talked. Remember?
就像我们第一次交谈一样。记住？
jiù   xiàng   wǒ   men   dì   yī   cì   jiāo   tán   yī   yàng   jì   zhù

575
00:41:11,013 --> 00:41:13,765
You knocked on my door with a look on your face -
你用脸上的脸敲了我的门 -
nǐ   yòng   liǎn   shàng   de   liǎn   qiāo   le   wǒ   de   mén

576
00:41:14,349 --> 00:41:18,478
You drove a nail in the wall and knocked my mirror down.
您在墙上开了钉子，把我的镜子撞倒了。
nín   zài   qiáng   shàng   kāi   le   dīng   zi   bǎ   wǒ   de   jìng   zi   zhuàng   dào   le

577
00:41:18,687 --> 00:41:20,689
Luckily it didn't break.
幸运的是，它没有破裂。
xìng   yùn   de   shì   tā   méi   yǒu   pò   liè

578
00:41:21,273 --> 00:41:24,443
"Who do you think you are? King of the universe?"
“你认为你是谁？宇宙之王？”
nǐ   rèn   wèi   nǐ   shì   shuí   yǔ   zhòu   zhī   wáng

579
00:41:24,610 --> 00:41:26,570
You were so rude to me.
你对我很无礼。
nǐ   duì   wǒ   hěn   wú   lǐ

580
00:41:26,737 --> 00:41:30,782
In two months you never once said hello on the stairs.
两个月后，您从未在楼梯上打招呼。
liǎng   gè   yuè   hòu   nín   cóng   wèi   zài   lóu   tī   shàng   dǎ   zhāo   hū

581
00:41:31,033 --> 00:41:33,202
It's been two years now.
已经两年了。
yǐ   jīng   liǎng   nián   le

582
00:41:33,368 --> 00:41:35,662
How long ago that seems now.
现在看起来多久了。
xiàn   zài   kàn   qǐ   lái   duō   jiǔ   le

583
00:41:35,829 --> 00:41:39,958
And how things have changed, though we were already at war then.
以及情况如何变化，尽管我们已经在战争中。
yǐ   jí   qíng   kuàng   rú   hé   biàn   huà   jǐn   guǎn   wǒ   men   yǐ   jīng   zài   zhàn   zhēng   zhōng

584
00:41:40,584 --> 00:41:43,420
Everyone foolishly thought it would be over quickly
每个人都愚蠢地以为会很快结束
měi   gè   rén   dōu   yú   chǔn   dì   yǐ   wèi   huì   hěn   kuài   jié   shù

585
00:41:43,587 --> 00:41:47,299
and that we'd only see it on newsreels.
而且我们只会在新闻媒体上看到它。
ér   qiě   wǒ   men   zhǐ   huì   zài   xīn   wén   méi   tǐ   shàng   kàn   dào   tā

586
00:41:47,466 --> 00:41:49,384
When is it going to end?
什么时候结束？
shén   me   shí   hòu   jié   shù

587
00:41:50,552 --> 00:41:53,514
Sometimes I just can't go on.
有时我只是不能继续。
yǒu   shí   wǒ   zhǐ   shì   bù   néng   jì   xù

588
00:41:54,848 --> 00:41:57,434
This winter feels like it will never end.
这个冬天感觉它永远不会结束。
zhè   gè   dōng   tiān   gǎn   jué   tā   yǒng   yuǎn   bù   huì   jié   shù

589
00:41:57,601 --> 00:41:59,603
It will end, Pina...
它将结束，pina ...
tā   jiāng   jié   shù

590
00:42:00,312 --> 00:42:02,314
and spring will come again,
春天会再次来
chūn   tiān   huì   zài   cì   lái

591
00:42:02,481 --> 00:42:06,193
more beautiful than ever, because we'll be free.
比以往任何时候都更美丽，因为我们会自由。
bǐ   yǐ   wǎng   rèn   hé   shí   hòu   dōu   gèng   měi   lì   yīn   wèi   wǒ   men   huì   zì   yóu

592
00:42:06,443 --> 00:42:09,279
We have to believe it and want it.
我们必须相信并想要它。
wǒ   men   bì   xū   xiāng   xìn   bìng   xiǎng   yào   tā

593
00:42:09,863 --> 00:42:12,825
I can feel these things inside,
我可以在里面感觉到这些东西，
wǒ   kě   yǐ   zài   lǐ   miàn   gǎn   jué   dào   zhè   xiē   dōng   xī

594
00:42:13,033 --> 00:42:15,118
but I can't explain them.
但是我无法解释他们。
dàn   shì   wǒ   wú   fǎ   jiě   shì   tā   men

595
00:42:15,285 --> 00:42:16,829
Manfredi could.
曼弗雷迪可以。
màn   fú   léi   dí   kě   yǐ

596
00:42:16,995 --> 00:42:20,707
He's an educated man who's been to college and traveled.
他是一个受过教育的人，去过大学并旅行。
tā   shì   yī   gè   shòu   guò   jiào   yù   de   rén   qù   guò   dà   xué   bìng   lǚ   xíng

597
00:42:21,208 --> 00:42:23,168
He can really talk well.
他真的可以说得很好。
tā   zhēn   de   kě   yǐ   shuō   dé   hěn   hǎo

598
00:42:23,335 --> 00:42:25,128
But I think it's like this:
但是我认为这样的是：
dàn   shì   wǒ   rèn   wèi   zhè   yàng   de   shì

599
00:42:25,295 --> 00:42:28,882
We mustn't be afraid now or in the future,
我们一定不要害怕现在或将来，
wǒ   men   yī   dìng   bù   yào   hài   pà   xiàn   zài   huò   jiāng   lái

600
00:42:29,091 --> 00:42:33,220
because we're on the just path. Understand, Pina?
因为我们走上了正当的道路。明白，皮纳？
yīn   wèi   wǒ   men   zǒu   shàng   le   zhèng   dāng   de   dào   lù   míng   bái   pí   nà

601
00:42:35,514 --> 00:42:38,225
We're fighting for something that has to be,
我们正在为必须做的事情而战
wǒ   men   zhèng   zài   wèi   bì   xū   zuò   de   shì   qíng   ér   zhàn

602
00:42:38,392 --> 00:42:40,394
that can't help coming.
不禁来。
bù   jìn   lái

603
00:42:40,936 --> 00:42:43,605
The road may be long and hard,
这条路可能漫长而艰难，
zhè   tiáo   lù   kě   néng   màn   zhǎng   ér   jiān   nán

604
