nín   bù   huì   wèi   nín   de   tiān   fù   ér   huò   dé   tài   duō   róng   yù

1130
01:26:19,022 --> 01:26:20,649
This will take a while.
这将需要一段时间。
zhè   jiāng   xū   yào   yī   duàn   shí   jiān

1131
01:26:20,857 --> 01:26:23,944
Come get me as soon as there's any news.
有任何消息，快来给我。
yǒu   rèn   hé   xiāo   xī   kuài   lái   gěi   wǒ

1132
01:26:24,444 --> 01:26:25,278
Come in.
进来。
jìn   lái

1133
01:26:28,573 --> 01:26:31,034
The deserter hanged himself, sir.
先生，逃兵吊死了。
xiān   shēng   táo   bīng   diào   sǐ   le

1134
01:26:31,201 --> 01:26:32,744
That idiot!
那个白痴！
nà   gè   bái   chī

1135
01:27:23,169 --> 01:27:25,797
- Who's winning? - Same as always.
- 谁赢了？ - 一如既往。
shuí   yíng   le   yī   rú   jì   wǎng

1136
01:27:45,942 --> 01:27:48,862
- Strenuous evening? - Not very...
- 剧烈的夜晚？ - 不是很...
jù   liè   de   yè   wǎn   bù   shì   hěn

1137
01:27:49,446 --> 01:27:50,697
but interesting.
但很有趣。
dàn   hěn   yǒu   qù

1138
01:27:50,864 --> 01:27:52,574
Really? How so?
真的吗？为何如此？
zhēn   de   ma   wèi   hé   rú   cǐ

1139
01:27:52,741 --> 01:27:55,577
I have a fellow who must talk before morning,
我有一个必须在早晨之前聊天的家伙，
wǒ   yǒu   yī   gè   bì   xū   zài   zǎo   chén   zhī   qián   liáo   tiān   de   jiā   huǒ

1140
01:27:56,411 --> 01:27:58,663
and an Italian priest who claims the fellow won't
一位声称同伴不会的意大利牧师
yī   wèi   shēng   chēng   tóng   bàn   bù   huì   de   yì   dà   lì   mù   shī

1141
01:27:58,830 --> 01:28:00,790
because he's praying for him.
因为他在为他祈祷。
yīn   wèi   tā   zài   wèi   tā   qí   dǎo

1142
01:28:00,957 --> 01:28:02,917
- And if he doesn't talk? - Ridiculous.
- 如果他不说话？ - 荒谬的。
rú   guǒ   tā   bù   shuō   huà   huāng   miù   de

1143
01:28:03,084 --> 01:28:05,086
If he won't talk no matter what?
如果他不会说什么？
rú   guǒ   tā   bù   huì   shuō   shén   me

1144
01:28:05,253 --> 01:28:09,758
That would mean an Italian is as good as a German...
那意味着意大利人和德国人一样好。
nà   yì   wèi   zhe   yì   dà   lì   rén   hé   dé   guó   rén   yī   yàng   hǎo

1145
01:28:10,550 --> 01:28:12,969
that there's no difference
没有区别
méi   yǒu   qū   bié

1146
01:28:13,136 --> 01:28:17,474
between the blood of a slave race and that of a master race.
在奴隶种族的鲜血和大师种族的血之间。
zài   nú   lì   zhǒng   zú   de   xiān   xuè   hé   dà   shī   zhǒng   zú   de   xuè   zhī   jiān

1147
01:28:21,603 --> 01:28:24,230
What would be the sense of our struggle?
我们斗争的感觉是什么？
wǒ   men   dòu   zhēng   de   gǎn   jué   shì   shén   me

1148
01:28:24,397 --> 01:28:28,318
Twenty-five years ago I led execution squads in France.
25年前，我领导了法国的处决小队。
nián   qián   wǒ   lǐng   dǎo   le   fǎ   guó   de   chù   jué   xiǎo   duì

1149
01:28:28,485 --> 01:28:30,445
I was a young officer then...
那时我是一名年轻军官...
nà   shí   wǒ   shì   yī   míng   nián   qīng   jūn   guān

1150
01:28:31,488 --> 01:28:34,282
and I too believed that we Germans were a master race.
我也相信我们的德国人是一场大师赛。
wǒ   yě   xiāng   xìn   wǒ   men   de   dé   guó   rén   shì   yī   chǎng   dà   shī   sài

1151
01:28:34,491 --> 01:28:38,453
But the French patriots chose to die rather than talk.
但是法国爱国者选择死而不是说话。
dàn   shì   fǎ   guó   ài   guó   zhě   xuǎn   zé   sǐ   ér   bù   shì   shuō   huà

1152
01:28:38,662 --> 01:28:42,582
We Germans refuse to realize that people want to be free.
我们德国人拒绝意识到人们想要自由。
wǒ   men   dé   guó   rén   jù   jué   yì   shí   dào   rén   men   xiǎng   yào   zì   yóu

1153
01:28:42,958 --> 01:28:46,211
- Hartmann, you're drunk! - Yes, I am.
- 哈特曼，你喝醉了！ - 我是。
hā   tè   màn   nǐ   hē   zuì   le   wǒ   shì

1154
01:28:46,795 --> 01:28:48,755
I drink every night to forget.
我每天晚上喝酒忘记。
wǒ   měi   tiān   wǎn   shàng   hē   jiǔ   wàng   jì

1155
01:28:48,922 --> 01:28:52,050
But instead I see more and more clearly.
但是，我越来越清楚地看到。
dàn   shì   wǒ   yuè   lái   yuè   qīng   chǔ   dì   kàn   dào

1156
01:28:52,425 --> 01:28:54,427
All we're really good at
我们真正擅长的
wǒ   men   zhēn   zhèng   shàn   zhǎng   de

1157
01:28:54,594 --> 01:28:56,763
is killing, killing, killing!
正在杀人，杀人，杀人！
zhèng   zài   shā   rén   shā   rén   shā   rén

1158
01:28:58,348 --> 01:29:01,017
We've strewn all of Europe with corpses,
我们已经用尸体散布在整个欧洲，
wǒ   men   yǐ   jīng   yòng   shī   tǐ   sàn   bù   zài   zhěng   gè   ōu   zhōu

1159
01:29:01,851 --> 01:29:06,273
and from their graves rises up an unquenchable hatred.
从他们的坟墓中提出了一种无法忍受的仇恨。
cóng   tā   men   de   fén   mù   zhōng   tí   chū   le   yī   zhǒng   wú   fǎ   rěn   shòu   de   chóu   hèn

1160
01:29:06,439 --> 01:29:09,401
Hatred... hatred everywhere!
仇恨...到处都是仇恨！
chóu   hèn   dào   chù   dōu   shì   chóu   hèn

1161
01:29:10,277 --> 01:29:13,989
That hatred will devour us. There's no hope.
这种仇恨会吞噬我们。没有希望。
zhè   zhǒng   chóu   hèn   huì   tūn   shì   wǒ   men   méi   yǒu   xī   wàng

1162
01:29:14,197 --> 01:29:14,948
Enough!
足够的！
zú   gòu   de

1163
01:29:15,365 --> 01:29:18,994
We'll all die without the slightest hope.
我们都没有丝毫希望而死。
wǒ   men   dōu   méi   yǒu   sī   háo   xī   wàng   ér   sǐ

1164
01:29:19,494 --> 01:29:21,788
I forbid you to continue!
我禁止你继续！
wǒ   jìn   zhǐ   nǐ   jì   xù

1165
01:29:23,623 --> 01:29:24,791
Without hope.
没有希望。
méi   yǒu   xī   wàng

1166
01:29:24,958 --> 01:29:27,544
You hear me? You forget that you are
你听到我的声音吗？你忘记了你是
nǐ   tīng   dào   wǒ   de   shēng   yīn   ma   nǐ   wàng   jì   le   nǐ   shì

1167
01:29:27,711 --> 01:29:29,337
a German officer!
德国军官！
dé   guó   jūn   guān

1168
01:29:34,843 --> 01:29:36,511
- Did he talk? - No, sir.
- 他说话了吗？ - 不，先生。
tā   shuō   huà   le   ma   bù   xiān   shēng

1169
01:29:36,678 --> 01:29:39,306
Wendel says he's never seen one so stubborn.
温德尔说，他从未见过如此固执。
wēn   dé   ěr   shuō   tā   cóng   wèi   jiàn   guò   rú   cǐ   gù   zhí

1170
01:29:39,472 --> 01:29:41,433
The man's gone completely numb.
该男子完全麻木了。
gāi   nán   zi   wán   quán   má   mù   le

1171
01:29:41,600 --> 01:29:43,602
What should we do now, sir?
先生，我们现在该怎么办？
xiān   shēng   wǒ   men   xiàn   zài   gāi   zěn   me   bàn

1172
01:30:00,327 --> 01:30:03,121
- Well? - It's impossible, sir.
- 出色地？ - 先生，这是不可能的。
chū   sè   dì   xiān   shēng   zhè   shì   bù   kě   néng   de

1173
01:30:03,288 --> 01:30:05,749
We have to let him regain some strength.
我们必须让他恢复一些力量。
wǒ   men   bì   xū   ràng   tā   huī   fù   yī   xiē   lì   liàng

1174
01:30:05,915 --> 01:30:07,792
Impossible! It's too late for that.
不可能的！为时已晚。
bù   kě   néng   de   wèi   shí   yǐ   wǎn

1175
01:30:07,959 --> 01:30:10,754
Shall we try psychological methods, sir?
先生，我们可以尝试心理方法吗？
xiān   shēng   wǒ   men   kě   yǐ   cháng   shì   xīn   lǐ   fāng   fǎ   ma

1176
01:30:10,920 --> 01:30:14,215
Are you crazy? He must talk now.
你疯了？他现在必须说话。
nǐ   fēng   le   tā   xiàn   zài   bì   xū   shuō   huà

1177
01:30:26,728 --> 01:30:28,188
Syringe.
注射器。
zhù   shè   qì

1178
01:30:56,007 --> 01:30:59,970
Mr. Ferraris, as I said before, I admire you greatly,
法拉利斯先生，正如我之前说的，我非常佩服你，
fǎ   lā   lì   sī   xiān   shēng   zhèng   rú   wǒ   zhī   qián   shuō   de   wǒ   fēi   cháng   pèi   fú   nǐ

1179
01:31:00,136 --> 01:31:03,306
and I do appreciate this proof of your courage
我很感谢您的勇气证明
wǒ   hěn   gǎn   xiè   nín   de   yǒng   qì   zhèng   míng

1180
01:31:03,473 --> 01:31:05,642
and spirit of sacrifice.
和牺牲精神。
hé   xī   shēng   jīng   shén

1181
01:31:05,809 --> 01:31:09,396
But you must understand: This can't go on.
但是您必须理解：这不能继续。
dàn   shì   nín   bì   xū   lǐ   jiě   zhè   bù   néng   jì   xù

1182
01:31:09,562 --> 01:31:11,606
You are a Communist.
你是共产党。
nǐ   shì   gòng   chǎn   dǎng

1183
01:31:11,815 --> 01:31:16,945
Your party has formed a pact with reactionary forces.
您的政党已与反动力量形成了协议。
nín   de   zhèng   dǎng   yǐ   yǔ   fǎn   dòng   lì   liàng   xíng   chéng   le   xié   yì

1184
01:31:17,362 --> 01:31:20,407
You're all working together against us now.
你们现在都在与我们一起工作。
nǐ   men   xiàn   zài   dōu   zài   yǔ   wǒ   men   yī   qǐ   gōng   zuò

1185
01:31:20,657 --> 01:31:23,994
But tomorrow, when Rome is occupied -
但是明天，当罗马被占领时 -
dàn   shì   míng   tiān   dāng   luó   mǎ   bèi   zhàn   lǐng   shí

1186
01:31:24,452 --> 01:31:27,414
or "liberated," as you call it -
或您称之为“解放”  -
huò   nín   chēng   zhī   wèi   jiě   fàng

1187
01:31:27,580 --> 01:31:31,835
will these monarchist officers still be your allies?
这些君主官员仍然会成为您的盟友吗？
zhè   xiē   jūn   zhǔ   guān   yuán   réng   rán   huì   chéng   wèi   nín   de   méng   yǒu   ma

1188
01:31:32,585 --> 01:31:34,879
I offer you the solution to this problem.
我为您提供解决这个问题的解决方案。
wǒ   wèi   nín   tí   gōng   jiě   jué   zhè   gè   wèn   tí   de   jiě   jué   fāng   àn

1189
01:31:36,172 --> 01:31:38,675
Give me the names of Badoglio's generals.
给我Badoglio将军的名字。
gěi   wǒ   jiāng   jūn   de   míng   zì

1190
01:31:38,842 --> 01:31:41,136
Help me arrest them,
帮我逮捕他们，
bāng   wǒ   dǎi   bǔ   tā   men

1191
01:31:41,303 --> 01:31:43,722
and I guarantee your release
我保证您的释放
wǒ   bǎo   zhèng   nín   de   shì   fàng

1192
01:31:43,888 --> 01:31:46,558
and immunity for the men in your party.
对您党中的男人的豁免权。
duì   nín   dǎng   zhōng   de   nán   rén   de   huō   miǎn   quán

1193
01:31:47,517 --> 01:31:49,311
Well, Mr. Ferraris?
好吧，法拉利斯先生？
hǎo   ba   fǎ   lā   lì   sī   xiān   shēng

1194
01:31:49,686 --> 01:31:51,479
Cursed dog!
被诅咒的狗！
bèi   zǔ   zhòu   de   gǒu

1195
01:31:53,440 --> 01:31:55,066
Keep at him till the end!
一直盯着他直到最后！
yī   zhí   dīng   zhe   tā   zhí   dào   zuì   hòu

1196
01:32:46,201 --> 01:32:47,535
How's it going?
怎么样了？
zěn   me   yàng   le

1197
01:32:47,744 --> 01:32:50,747
I told you it wouldn't be so easy.
我告诉你，这并不容易。
wǒ   gào   sù   nǐ   zhè   bìng   bù   róng   yì

1198
01:33:32,038 --> 01:33:33,581
A cigarette.
香烟。
xiāng   yān

1199
01:34:02,694 --> 01:34:04,362
The priest, quick!
牧师，很快！
mù   shī   hěn   kuài

1200
01:34:12,329 --> 01:34:15,123
Look, priest! Satisfied now?
看，牧师！现在满意吗？
kàn   mù   shī   xiàn   zài   mǎn   yì   ma

1201
01:34:15,290 --> 01:34:16,916
This is your Christian charity.
这是您的基督教慈善机构。
zhè   shì   nín   de   jī   dū   jiào   cí   shàn   jī   gòu

1202
01:34:17,083 --> 01:34:19,919
This is your love for your brother in Christ.
这是您对基督兄弟的爱。
zhè   shì   nín   duì   jī   dū   xiōng   dì   de   ài

1203
01:34:20,086 --> 01:34:23,173
You preferred to see him like this rather than talk.
您更喜欢看到他这样而不是说话。
nín   gèng   xǐ   huān   kàn   dào   tā   zhè   yàng   ér   bù   shì   shuō   huà

1204
01:34:23,340 --> 01:34:27,260
But don't think you'll save yourself, you hypocrite,
但是不要以为你会拯救自己，你伪君子，
dàn   shì   bù   yào   yǐ   wèi   nǐ   huì   zhěng   jiù   zì   jǐ   nǐ   wěi   jūn   zi

1205
01:34:27,427 --> 01:34:30,305
or your accomplices either. You'll die a traitor's death.
或您的同伙。你会死一个叛徒的死。
huò   nín   de   tóng   huǒ   nǐ   huì   sǐ   yī   gè   pàn   tú   de   sǐ

1206
01:34:30,847 --> 01:34:32,474
We'll destroy you all,
我们会摧毁你们所有人，
wǒ   men   huì   cuī   huǐ   nǐ   men   suǒ   yǒu   rén

1207
01:34:32,682 --> 01:34:34,726
to the last man!
到最后一个男人！
dào   zuì   hòu   yī   gè   nán   rén

1208
01:34:35,644 --> 01:34:37,395
You didn't talk.
你没有说话。
nǐ   méi   yǒu   shuō   huà

1209
01:35:20,772 --> 01:35:23,275
It is finished.
它完成了。
tā   wán   chéng   le

1210
01:35:24,901 --> 01:35:28,071
You tried to destroy his soul, but you only destroyed his body!
您试图摧毁他的灵魂，但您只摧毁了他的身体！
nín   shì   tú   cuī   huǐ   tā   de   líng   hún   dàn   nín   zhǐ   cuī   huǐ   le   tā   de   shēn   tǐ

1211
01:35:28,613 --> 01:35:29,823
Curse you all!
诅咒你们所有人！
zǔ   zhòu   nǐ   men   suǒ   yǒu   rén

1212
01:35:30,323 --> 01:35:31,283
Curse you all!
诅咒你们所有人！
zǔ   zhòu   nǐ   men   suǒ   yǒu   rén

1213
01:35:32,826 --> 01:35:34,703
You'll be trampled in the dust like worms!
您会像蠕虫一样被践踏尘土！
nín   huì   xiàng   rú   chóng   yī   yàng   bèi   jiàn   tà   chén   tǔ

1214
01:35:35,161 --> 01:35:36,121
Curse you all!
诅咒你们所有人！
zǔ   zhòu   nǐ   men   suǒ   yǒu   rén

1215
01:35:44,921 --> 01:35:46,381
My God...
我的上帝...
wǒ   de   shàng   dì

1216
01:35:47,257 --> 01:35:49,259
what have I said?
我说了什么？
wǒ   shuō   le   shén   me

1217
01:35:50,260 --> 01:35:54,014
Forgive me, Lord.
请原谅我，主。
qǐng   yuán   liàng   wǒ   zhǔ

1218
01:36:16,578 --> 01:36:17,537
Out!
出去！
chū   qù

1219
01:36:17,704 --> 01:36:19,372
Take the priest back!
带牧师！
dài   mù   shī

1220
01:36:19,539 --> 01:36:21,708
Everybody out, now!
每个人都出去了！
měi   gè   rén   dōu   chū   qù   le

1221
01:36:22,334 --> 01:36:24,377
Stupid Italians!
愚蠢的意大利人！
yú   chǔn   de   yì   dà   lì   rén

1222
01:36:25,503 --> 01:36:28,548
Damn it! We failed.
该死的！我们失败了。
gāi   sǐ   de   wǒ   men   shī   bài   le

1223
01:36:28,715 --> 01:36:30,675
That damned priest got me flustered.
那该死的牧师让我感到慌张。
nà   gāi   sǐ   de   mù   shī   ràng   wǒ   gǎn   dào   huāng   zhāng

1224
01:36:30,842 --> 01:36:33,011
I told you it wouldn't be easy.
我告诉你，这并不容易。
wǒ   gào   sù   nǐ   zhè   bìng   bù   róng   yì

1225
01:36:33,178 --> 01:36:35,347
You're always right.
你总是对的。
nǐ   zǒng   shì   duì   de

1226
01:36:35,513 --> 01:36:37,349
The report, sir?
报告，先生？
bào   gào   xiān   shēng

1227
01:36:37,515 --> 01:36:40,352
Ah, yes. "Cause of death:
啊，是的。 “死亡原因：
a   shì   de   sǐ   wáng   yuán   yīn

1228
01:36:41,436 --> 01:36:43,063
Heart attack."
心脏病发作。”
xīn   zàng   bìng   fā   zuò

1229
01:36:43,563 --> 01:36:45,315
Yes, sir. And the young woman?
是的，先生。还有年轻的女人？
shì   de   xiān   shēng   hái   yǒu   nián   qīng   de   nǚ   rén

1230
01:36:45,649 --> 01:36:46,900
That's up to the lady.
这取决于女士。
zhè   qǔ   jué   yú   nǚ   shì

1231
01:36:47,067 --> 01:36:49,486
Lock her up a while and then -
将她锁定一会儿，然后 -
jiāng   tā   suǒ   dìng   yī   huì   ér   rán   hòu

1232
